INSERT INTO `healthtipfivep4s` VALUES (1,'Clean pillow cases and sheets','清洗床單和被單','清洗床单和被单','Clean out the clutter','清潔雜物','清洁杂物','Choose anti-allergy sheets and pillow cases','挑選防敏床單及枕頭套','挑选防敏床单及枕头套','0000-00-00 00:00:00','2015-10-09 02:23:42','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<p><strong>Dust Mite</strong></p>\n\n<p>Dust Mites are perhaps the most common cause of allergies.&nbsp; They thrive in mattresses, bedding, upholstered furniture, carpeting and any other household fabrics, such as curtains and drapes.</p>\n\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:square\">\n	<li>Wash sheets and blankets regularly in hot water</li>\n	<li>Reduce clutter and dust with a damp cloth each week</li>\n	<li>Use synthetic mattress pads and pillows</li>\n	<li>Use zippered dust-proof covers on mattresses and pillows</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><a href=\"http://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%A1%B5%E8%9F%8E\">塵蟎</a>是肉眼看不見的微小生物，喜歡在溫暖潮濕的環境生活。牠身上亦帶有致敏蛋白，可於人類身上引致過敏的症狀。<a href=\"http://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%A1%B5%E8%9F%8E\">塵蟎</a>會藏身於床褥，被單，地毯，窗簾等地方。想改善情況可注意以下事項：</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:square\">\n	<li>每星期用熱水清洗床單和被單</li>\n	<li>每星期用濕布清潔雜物</li>\n	<li>使用合成物質的床褥及枕頭</li>\n	<li>挑選有防塵功能的床單及枕頭套</li>\n</ul>\n','<p>尘螨是肉眼看不见的微小生物，喜欢在温暖潮湿的环境生活。它身上亦带有致敏蛋白，可于人类身上引致过敏的症状。尘螨会藏身于床褥，被单，地毯，窗帘等地方。想改善情况可注意以下事项：</p>\n\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:square\">\n	<li>每星期用热水清洗床单和被单</li>\n	<li>每星期用湿布清洁杂物</li>\n	<li>使用合成物质的床褥及枕头</li>\n	<li>挑选有防尘功能的床单及枕头套</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>Dust Mite</strong></p>\n\n<p>Dust Mites are perhaps the most common cause of allergies.&nbsp; They thrive in mattresses, bedding, upholstered furniture, carpeting and any other household fabrics, such as curtains and drapes.</p>\n\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:square\">\n	<li>Wash sheets and blankets regularly in hot water</li>\n	<li>Reduce clutter and dust with a damp cloth each week</li>\n	<li>Use synthetic mattress pads and pillows</li>\n	<li>Use zippered dust-proof covers on mattresses and pillows</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><a href=\"http://zh.wikipedi