INSERT INTO `healthtipfours` VALUES (1,'Cough is a natural reflex of the body that can facilitate better breathing by clearing the airways.  The function of cough is to protect the lungs from irritating substances.  It is normal to cough a little bit sometimes.  However, chronic cough indicates that there may be problems in the respiratory system or other parts of the human body.\n\nCough can either be productive which produces excessive mucus or phlegm, or non-productive which has no mucus or phlegm. Non-productive cough can be described as dry cough which is caused by inflammation of the upper airway due to dust, foreign bodies or a throat infection.  \n','咳嗽是身體保護肺部免受刺激源侵害的一種自然反射。當你的氣管有分泌物時，可通過咳嗽將分泌物清出，使呼吸暢順。偶然有少許咳嗽是正常的，可是持續或强烈的咳嗽，就可能表示呼吸系統出現毛病或身體其他因素出現問題。\n\n咳嗽可分為兩種 - 乾咳和痰咳。簡單來說，痰咳指帶有因呼吸道受刺激而分泌痰液的咳嗽；而乾咳則相反，指沒帶有痰液的咳嗽。','咳嗽是身体保护肺部免受刺激源侵害的一种自然反射。当你的气管有分泌物时，可通过咳嗽将分泌物清出，使呼吸畅顺。偶然有少许咳嗽是正常的，可是持续或强烈的咳嗽，就可能表示呼吸系统出现毛病或身体其他因素出现问题。\n\n咳嗽可分为两种 - 乾咳和痰咳。简单来说，痰咳指带有因呼吸道受刺激而分泌痰液的咳嗽；而乾咳则相反，指没带有痰液的咳嗽。','<p><strong>Common causes of cough:</strong></p>\n\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:square\">\n	<li>Entry of foreign substances into the respiratory tract, such as nasal discharge, food, water or dust.</li>\n	<li>Inhalation of irritating gas such as smoke and exhaust gas.</li>\n	<li>Infection of virus or bacteria, such as flu.</li>\n	<li>Allergic reactions such as allergic asthma.</li>\n	<li>Respiratory tract diseases such as bronchitis, tracheitis, pneumonia, tuberculosis and emphysema.</li>\n	<li>Irritation of respiratory tract such as&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height:20.8px\">acid regurgitation, which may lead to n</span>ight cough</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Natural remedies</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Drink water and avoid caffeine and alcohol.</li>\n	<li>Dry air in winter may irritate our throats. &nbsp;A humidifier can help relieving congestion and breathing.</li>\n	<li>If cough is due to acid regurgitation, it is advisable to elevate the head of your bed with a pillow during sleeping.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Avoid eating or drinking 2-3 hours before sleeping.</li>\n	<li>If cough persists for 2-3 weeks, or is accompanied with fever, shortness of breath or blood in the mucus, seek medical advice immediately.</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>常見的咳嗽原因</strong></p>\n\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:square\">\n	<li>異物誤入氣管，例如鼻水, 食物, 水及灰塵。</li>\n	<li>吸入刺激性氣體，例如煙霧及廢氣。</li>\n	<li>病毒或細菌感染，例如感冒。</li>\n	<li>過敏反應，例如過敏性氣喘。</li>\n	<li>支氣管炎、氣管炎、肺炎、肺結核、肺氣腫等呼吸道疾病。</li>\n	<li><span style=\"line-height:20.8px\">氣管受到<span style=\"line-height:20.8px\">剌激，</span>如</span><span style=\"line-height:20.8px\">食道胃酸逆流，導致</span>夜間咳嗽。</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>咳嗽的自然療法</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>多飲水，避免含咖啡因及酒精的飲料。</li>\n	<li>秋冬季空氣乾燥容易刺激咽喉。嘗試使用空氣增濕器加濕空氣，對乾燥的咽喉有滋潤作用。</li>\n	<li>若咳嗽由胃酸倒流引起，可嘗試睡眠時將床頭稍為升高或加多一個枕頭。</li>\n	<li>睡前的2至3小時內禁飲食。</li>\n	<li>如果咳嗽超過2至3星期，或同時有發燒、呼吸急促或有血痰，應立即看醫生。</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>常见的咳嗽原因</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>异物误入气管，例如鼻水, 食物, 水及灰尘。</li>\n	<li>吸入刺激性气体，例如烟雾及废气。</li>\n	<li>病毒或细菌感染，例如感冒。</li>\n	<li>过敏反应，例如过敏性的气喘。</li>\n	<li>支气管炎、气管炎、肺炎、肺结核、肺气肿等呼吸道疾病。</li>\n	<li>气管受到剌激，如食道胃酸逆流，导致夜间咳嗽。</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>咳嗽的自然疗法</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>多饮水，避免含咖啡因及酒精的饮料。</li>\n	<li>秋冬季空气乾燥容易刺激咽喉。尝试使用空气增湿器加湿空气，对乾燥的咽喉有滋润作用。</li>\n	<li>若咳嗽由于胃酸倒流引起，可尝试睡眠时将床头稍为升高或加多一个枕头。</li>\n	<li>睡前的2至3小时内禁饮食。</li>\n	<li>如果咳嗽超过2至3星期，或同时有发烧、呼吸急促或有血痰，应立即看医生。</li>\n</ul>\n','0000-00-00 00:00:00','2015-10-09 02:15:38','0000-00-00 00:00:00');
