INSERT INTO `healthtipsixes` VALUES (1,'Heartburn is so common that many people have it at least a few times a year.  It’s a burning and painful feeling in the chest.   This happens when the gastric acids leak up from stomach into esophagus and causes irritation. You might feel heartburn only for a few moments or as long as couple of hours.  Smoking, drinking, eating certain kinds of food or wearing clothes that are too tight can contribute to the onset of heartburn.  ','“火燒心”十分普遍的症狀，一般人每年都會經歷數次胸口灼熱和疼痛。“火燒心”其實是胃酸過多,胃酸從胃部流到食道的症狀；而持續的時間由數分鐘至數小時不等。吸煙、飲酒及進食刺激性食物、穿著太緊身衣物等都是導致“火燒心”原因。“火燒心”通常發生在睡眠前進食；這樣的不適嚴重時影響睡眠質素，也因此而導致壓力, 影響生活。','“火烧心”十分普遍的症状，一般人每年都会经历数次胸口灼热和疼痛。“火烧心”其实是胃酸过多,胃酸从胃部流到食道的症状；而持续的时间由数分钟至数小时不等。吸烟、饮酒及进食刺激性食物、穿着太紧身衣物等都是导致“火烧心”原因。“火烧心”通常发生在睡眠前进食；这样的不适严重时影响睡眠质素，也因此而导致压力, 影响生活。','<p>Antacids work by neutralizing acid that causes heartburn. &nbsp;The ingredients Aluminium Hydroxide and Magnesium Hydroxide in Magsil neutralize the stomach acidity that irritates the esophagus.&nbsp; The advantage of taking antacids is that they start neutralizing stomach acid as soon as they contact it.&nbsp; They do not have to be absorbed into the bloodstream before they start working.</p>\n','<p>解酸劑是以中和胃酸原理 減低火燒心的不適, 幸福胃的素含有 Aluminum Hydroxide 及 Magnesium Hydroxide, 有效中和胃酸, 舒緩胃酸倒流的情況。 服用幸福胃的素的 好處是此成份到達胃部便會直接發揮效用, 而無需被血液吸收。</p>\n','<p>CHS</p>\n','<p>Antacids work by neutralizing acid that causes heartburn. &nbsp;The ingredients Aluminium Hydroxide and Magnesium Hydroxide in Magsil neutralize the stomach acidity that irritates the esophagus.&nbsp; The advantage of taking antacids is that they start neutralizing stomach acid as soon as they contact it.&nbsp; They do not have to be absorbed into the bloodstream before they start working.</p>\n','<p>Antacids work by neutralizing acid that causes heartburn. &nbsp;The ingredients Aluminium Hydroxide and Magnesium Hydroxide in Magsil neutralize the stomach acidity that irritates the esophagus.&nbsp; The advantage of taking antacids is that