INSERT INTO `healthtiptwop2s` VALUES (1,'<p><strong>Children&#39;s cold &amp; flu relief tips</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Give your child plenty of fluids which can help thining mucus, relieving nasal congestion and sore throat.</li>\n	<li>Use cool mist vaporizer in your child&rsquo;s bedroom to relieve coughing as it often gets worse at night.</li>\n	<li>For young children, raise the head of the crib to prevent post nasal drip and to ease nasal congestion and coughing.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Children&#39;s cold &amp; flu prevention tips</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Ensure you and your child wash hands frequently to reduce the spread of germs.</li>\n	<li>Avoid your child from sharing food, utensils and toothbrushes with other children.</li>\n	<li>Clean yuor children&#39;s plastic toys as the children may put them in their mouths regularly.</li>\n	<li>Spend more time with your children when they are suffering from flu, as what he/she needs most is love and care from parents.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>No matter how old a child is, always keep his/her respiratory tract clear. &nbsp;Teach them how to blow the nose so as to avoid post nasal drip.</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>舒緩傷風小貼士</strong></p>\n\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:square\">\n	<li>給小孩多飲水或菓汁，有助稀釋黏膜，舒緩鼻塞及喉嚨痛。</li>\n	<li>通常咳嗽在夜間比較嚴重，影響睡眠之餘亦會影響病人康復。 可試試在小孩的睡房使用蒸氣噴霧機，可幫助減輕咳嗽及鼻塞問題。</li>\n	<li>睡眠時, 用枕頭升高小孩床的頭部位置，有助防止鼻水倒流，亦可舒緩鼻塞及咳嗽。</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>預防傷風小貼士</strong></p>\n\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:square\">\n	<li>小孩或照顧小孩的人都要勤洗手，減低病菌傳播的機會。</li>\n	<li>避免小孩與其他小朋友分享同一份食物、共用同一器皿或牙刷等，避免病菌傳播。</li>\n	<li>小孩常常會將塑膠玩具放入口中，因此要注意經常清洗該些玩具。</li>\n	<li>小朋友不舒服時，最需要是父母關懷呵護。抱著他或安排他在能看到你的地方總比他一個人在房間好，亦能令小朋友安心。</li>\n	<li>無論那個年紀的孩子，應保持呼吸道清潔。 當孩子長大，就要教他們噴鼻, 減少鼻水倒流至喉嚨。</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>舒缓伤风小秘方</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>给小孩多饮水或菓汁，有助稀释黏膜，舒缓鼻塞及喉咙痛。</li>\n	<li>通常咳嗽在夜间比较严重，影响睡眠之余亦会影响病人康复。 可试试在小孩的睡房使用蒸气喷雾机，可帮助减轻咳嗽及鼻塞问题。</li>\n	<li>睡眠时, 用枕头升高小孩床的头部位置，有助防止鼻水倒流，亦可舒缓鼻塞及咳嗽。</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>预防伤风小秘方</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>小孩或照顾