INSERT INTO `healthtiptwos` VALUES (1,'Colds are caused by viruses that are transmitted from person to person with a sneeze or a cough.  It is estimated that most babies get inflected around 10 times a year in the first one or two years after birth.  When the flu is recovered, the child will get the immunity to that strain of virus.  When children reach 4 years old, they have built up sufficient immunity against certain kind of virus. The number of times of catching cold or flu is reduced to 6.','兒童傷風 \n傷風是由過濾性病毒引起的，可以藉著打噴嚏或咳嗽人傳人。大多數小兒在出世後頭1或2年，每年都會患上大約10次傷風。當小孩們患上傷風以後，他們就會對該特定的病毒產生免疫力。到小孩們長大到3、4歲左右，他們一般巳經累積了一定的抵抗力，患傷風的次數亦會減低到每年只有6次左右。\n','CHS','<p><strong>Tips to easing child&rsquo;s cold symptoms</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Be sure to give your child plenty of fluids which can help thining mucus, relieve stuffy noses and soothe sore throats.</li>\n	<li>Use a cool mist vaporizer in your child&rsquo;s bedroom to relieve coughing which often gets worse at night.</li>\n	<li>For young children, raise the head of the crib to prevent post nasal drip and to ease congestion and coughing.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Tips to prevent child&rsquo;s cold and flu</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Make sure your child wash his hands often to reduce the spread of germs</li>\n	<li>Discourage your child from sharing food, utensils and toothbrushes with other children</li>\n	<li>Wash plastic toys that children put in their mouths regularly</li>\n	<li>When a child is suffering from the symptoms of flu, what he or she needs most is tender love and care from parents.&nbsp; Therefore, it&rsquo;s better to put him/her on the couch near you.</li>\n	<li>No matter how old a child is, try to keep his/her respiratory tract clear.&nbsp; As the child grows up, teach him/her how to blow the nose so as to avoid post nasal drip.</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>舒緩傷風小貼士</strong></p>\n\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:square\">\n	<li>給小孩多飲開水或菓汁，此舉有助稀化黏膜，對舒緩鼻塞及喉嚨痛有幫助。</li>\n	<li>通常咳嗽在夜間比較嚴重，但是睡眠對病人康復是十分重要。 可試試在小孩的睡房使用蒸氣噴