INSERT INTO `historyintros` VALUES (1,'<p><strong>Vision &amp; Mission1</strong></p>\n\n<p>To be your most trusted companion: restoring, safeguarding and improving the health / wellbeing of everyone we touch in the most ever-present, caring and self-improving manner.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Our Brand</strong></p>\n\n<p>We vow to go one step further and excel in every market we operate in. We provide high value and extensive product lines in the most accessible fashion by leveraging knowledge and experience from our long successful history.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Our values to Customers</strong></p>\n\n<p>We are aspired to be the most trustworthy and reliable alliance to you, our customers. We do everything to understand your needs and to better ourselves. It is also our responsibility to hold in high esteem customer loyalty and business sustainability for ourselves and partners.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Our values to Products</strong></p>\n\n<p>We are committed to enhancing the efficacy and quality of our products to meet with the ever-changing global regulatory landscape and to investing in diversification and innovation in our product portfolio to meet you, our customers&rsquo; dynamic needs.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Our values to Our People</strong></p>\n\n<p>We shall continuously care for you, our people, develop you to be the best in the field and facilitate harmony within the organisation. Fortune is dedicated to being one family with a professional working environment.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Our values to Community</strong></p>\n\n<p>We believe we are more than just a business. We also give our care to our partners and help build you, our community a better</p>\n','<p><strong>願景和使命</strong></p>\n\n<p>幸福醫藥不斷求進，守護大眾身心健康，成為您最值得信賴的伙伴。</p>\n\n<p><strong>我們的品牌</strong></p>\n\n<p>代表我們多年來累積的經驗及知識，以優秀及多元化的產品，切合不同市場所需，凡事都會多走一步，成為大眾心目中的卓越品牌。</p>\n\n<p><strong>我們對顧客的承諾</strong></p>\n\n<p>致力成為您最可靠及值得信賴的伙伴，用心聆聽您的需要，從而作出改善，您多年來的支持，成為我們的推動力，使我們不斷精益求精。</p>\n\n<p><strong>我們對產品的保証</strong></p>\n\n<p>我們承諾提升產品的質量和效用，與時並進，達致世界性標準；不斷研發，推出更多產品，切合不同需要。</p>\n\n<p><strong>我們對員工的承諾</strong></p>\n\n<p>我們重視您 － 每位員工的發展，致力栽培您成為行業的精英；在和諧幸福家庭中，培育專業人才。</p>\n\n<p><strong>我們對社會的承諾</strong></p>\n\n<p>我們肩負社會責任，在不同領域作出貢獻，為社會帶來更好的明天。</p>\n','<p><strong>愿景和使命</strong></p>\n\n<p>幸福医药不断求进，守护大众身心健康，成为您最值得信赖的伙伴。</p>\n\n<p><strong>我们的品牌</strong></p>\n\n<p>代表我们多年来累积的经验及知识，以优秀及多元化的产品，切合不同市场所需，凡事都会多走一步，成为大众心目中的卓越品牌。</p>\n\n<p><strong>我们对顾客的承诺</strong></p>\n\n<p>致力成为您最可靠及值得信赖的伙伴，用心聆听您的需要，从而作出改善，您多年来的支持，成为我们的推动力，使我们不断精益求精。</p>\n\n<p><strong>我们对产品的保証</strong></p>\n\n<p>我们承诺提升产品的质量和效用，与时并进，达致世界性标準；不断研发，推出更多产品，切合不同需要。</p>\n\n<p><strong>我们对员工的承诺</strong></p>\n\n<p>我们重视您 － 每位员工的发展，致力栽培您成为行业的精英；在和谐幸福家庭中，培育专业人才。</p>\n\n<p><strong>我们对社会的承诺</strong></p>\n\n<p>我们肩负社会责任，在不同领域作出贡献，为社会带来更好的明天。</p>\n','njIQiD5SQtQ','XMzE4NzcxNjE2','0000-00-00 00:00:00','2016-11-17 21:16:35','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','','njIQiD5SQtQ','njIQiD5SQtQ','HAHAHAHHAHAHA','B9PIWJG7o3bkBwpY5atpGxxvDTa4Dzgu.jpg','<p>Established our brand value through creating the company motto &quot;Always go one step further&quot; and matching advertising</p>\n','<p>创立「幸福要行多步」公司口号，配合广告宣传，成功确立品牌价值</p>\n','<p>創立「幸福要行多步」公司口號，配合廣告宣傳，成功確立品牌價值</p>\n');
