INSERT INTO `newposts` VALUES (1,'Fortune Pharmacal\'s \"Lion Rock Spirit\" TVC received 4 awards at the \"TVB Most Popular TV Commercial Awards 2015\"','幸福醫藥廣告- 獅子山精神囊括 2015「TVB 最受歡迎廣告大獎」四大獎項 ','幸福医药广告- 狮子山精神囊括 2015「TVB 最受欢迎广告大奖」四大奖项 ','<p>The&nbsp;inspirational branding commercial &quot;Lion Rock Spirit&quot; of Fortune Pharmacal has received 4 awards at the &quot;TVB Most Popular TV Commercial Awards 2015&quot;!</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Awards include:</p>\n\n<p><strong>Professional Selection Awards</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Most Creative Award</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Best Visual Effects Award</strong></p>\n\n<p>and last but not least is the</p>\n\n<p>**<strong>Best of the Best Award</strong>**&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Thank you for your support and vote!</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','<p>幸福醫藥廣告 - 獅子山精神於「TVB最受歡迎廣告大獎頒獎典禮」, 幸福醫藥廣告 - 獅子山精神囊括了四項大獎 !</p>\n\n<p>包括 :</p>\n\n<p><strong>專業評審獎</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>最具創意大獎</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>最佳視覺效果大獎</strong></p>\n\n<p>與及全晚最高殊榮 :</p>\n\n<p><strong>**</strong><strong>至尊榮譽大獎**</strong></p>\n\n<p>多謝大家支持及投票 !</p>\n','<p>幸福医药广告 - 狮子山精神于「TVB最受欢迎广告大奖颁奖典礼」, 幸福医药广告 - 狮子山精神囊括了四项大奖 !</p>\n\n<p>包括 :</p>\n\n<p><strong>专业评审奖</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>最具创意大奖</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>最佳视觉效果大奖</strong></p>\n\n<p>与及全晚最高殊荣 :</p>\n\n<p><strong>**至尊荣誉大奖**</strong></p>\n\n<p>多谢大家支持及投票 !</p>\n','ypB2JLk4gTbDCIKzE8leqKd9IH9eK2b4.jpg','2015-07-07',0,'2015-04-27 04:17:47','2017-01-27 11:00:40','0000-00-00 00:00:00','ypB2JLk4gTbDCIKzE8leqKd9IH9eK2b4.jpg','','',0),(2,'Beware of Unauthorised Sales Platforms','慎防未經授權銷售平台','慎防未經授權銷售平台','<p>In order to safeguard customers&rsquo; interests, Fortune Pharmacal declares it has no connection with these unauthorised sales platforms. The official name of company is &lsquo;Fortune Pharmacal Co Ltd&rsquo;.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Our official website is <a href=\"http://www.fortunepharm.com/\">http://www.fortunepharm.com/</a>.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Should you have any enquiry, pleas