INSERT INTO `products` VALUES (1,'COLTALIN','幸福傷風素','幸福伤风素','Recovery forumla for colds, flu and allergy','收鼻水/抗過敏/傷風感冒配方','收鼻水/抗过敏/伤风感冒配方','<ul>\n	<li>Fast and effective relief of cold &amp; flu symptoms including sneezing, runny nose, fever, nasal congestion, muscular pains and headache.</li>\n	<li>Aspirin free - less likely to cause gastric discomfort.</li>\n	<li>Contains Vitamin B1 which promotes carbohydrate metabolism and maintains normal functioning of the cardiovascular, nervous and digestive systems.</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>有效迅速舒緩因傷風感冒引起之症狀，包括噴嚏、流鼻水、發燒、鼻塞、肌肉酸痛及頭痛等不適。</li>\n	<li>不含亞士匹靈，甚少引致腸胃不適。</li>\n	<li>加入維他命B1，促進碳水化合物的新陳代謝，維持心臟血管、神經和消化系統的正常功能。</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>有效迅速舒缓因伤风感冒引起之症状，包括喷嚏丶流鼻水丶发烧丶鼻塞丶肌肉酸痛及头痛等不适。</li>\n	<li>不含阿司匹林，甚少引致肠胃不适。</li>\n	<li>加入维他命B1，促进碳水化合物的新陈代谢，维持心脏血管丶神经和消化系统的正常功能。</li>\n</ul>\n','XK9NdrFoDJvJigW00j3BZKQb2IVxfSJ6.png','zKibHdvshKMb2Df1qaDw5tVmNjBtaAU3.png','MmoAB9yfPWxPxO6klP7FhuVktEQyTlPF.png',1,1,'HK-09667',50,'<ul>\n	<li>Available in packs of 12, 24 and&nbsp;36 tablets</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>藥片</li>\n	<li>12片裝，24片裝及36片裝</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>药片</li>\n	<li>12片装，24片装及36片装</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>Age: </strong>Adults &amp; children over 12 years<br />\n<strong>Dosage and Administration:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Two tablets every 4 hours</li>\n	<li>not to exceed eight tablets in 24 hours</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Remarks：Take each dose with plenty of water.</strong></p>\n','<p><strong>歳數：</strong>成人及12歲以上兒童<br />\n<strong>劑量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每次服兩片 ,每4小時服一次</li>\n	<li>24小時內不可服用超過八片</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>備註：服用時宜多飲開水。</strong></p>\n','<p><strong>岁数：</strong>成人及12岁以上儿童<br />\n<strong>剂量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每次服两片, 每4小时服1次</li>\n	<li>24小时内不可服用超过八片</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>备注：服用时宜多饮开水。</strong></p>\n','<p><strong>Each tablet contains:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Paracetamol (Acetaminophen) 250mg</strong><br />\nPurpose: Relieves pain &amp; fever</p>\n\n<p><strong>Chlorpheniramine Maleate 2mg</strong><br />\nPurpose:&nbsp;Relieves allergic symptoms such as runny nose, sneezing, watery eyes and itchy eyes</p>\n\n<p><strong>Phenylephrine Hydrochloride 5mg</strong><br />\nPurpose: Relieves nasal congestion and eases breathing</p>\n\n<p><strong>Thiamine Hydrochloride (Vitamin B1) 3mg</strong><br />\nPurpose:&nbsp;Promotes carbohydrate metabolism and maintains normal functioning of the cardiovascular, nervous and digestive systems</p>\n\n<p><strong>Caffeine Anhydrous 30mg</strong><br />\nPurpose:&nbsp;Improves wakefulness and relieves tiredness caused by cold &amp; flu</p>\n','<p><strong>每片含量：</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>撲熱息痛 (對乙酰氨基酚) 250毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 止痛退燒，減輕頭痛、肌肉酸痛及咽喉痛等症狀</p>\n\n<p><strong>馬來酸氯苯那敏 2毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒緩流鼻水、打噴嚏、淚眼及眼部痕癢等過敏症狀</p>\n\n<p><strong>鹽酸去氧腎上腺素 5毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒緩鼻塞，令呼吸更為暢順</p>\n\n<p><strong>鹽酸硫胺 (維他命B1) 3毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 促進碳水化合物的新陳代謝，維持心臟血管、神經和消化系統的正常功能</p>\n\n<p><strong>無水咖啡因 30毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 有助提神及舒緩傷風感冒引起的疲倦</p>\n','<p><strong>每片含量：</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>扑热息痛 (对乙酰氨基酚) 250毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 止痛退烧，减轻头痛、肌肉酸痛及咽喉痛等症状</p>\n\n<p><strong>马来酸氯苯那敏 2毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒缓流鼻水、打喷嚏、泪眼及眼部痕痒等过敏症状</p>\n\n<p><strong>盐酸去氧肾上腺素 5毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒缓鼻塞，令呼吸更为畅顺</p>\n\n<p><strong>维生素B1 3毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 促进碳水化合物的新陈代谢，维持心脏血管、神经和消化系统的正常功能</p>\n\n<p><strong>无水咖啡因 30毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 有助提神及舒缓伤风感冒引起的疲倦</p>\n','<ul>\n	<li>This may cause drowsiness. If affected, do not drive or operate machinery.</li>\n	<li>Inappropriate use of this medicine has the potential to cause liver toxicity or severe liver damage.&nbsp;Do not exceed the stated dose.&nbsp;Do not take with any other drug containing paracetamol unless advised by a healthcare professional.&nbsp;<strong>COLTALIN TABLET&nbsp;is safe and reliable</strong>&nbsp;if the stated &quot;Dosage &amp; Administration&quot; is followed.</li>\n	<li>Consult your doctor before use if :\n	<ul>\n		<li>you are under the care of a doctor</li>\n		<li>you are receiving prescribed medications</li>\n		<li>you are pregnant or are breastfeeding</li>\n		<li>you have kidney or liver disease</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Avoid alcoholic drink.</li>\n	<li>Do not take this product if you are hypersensitive to any ingredient of this product.</li>\n	<li>If the symptoms persist, or get worse, seek medical advice immediately.</li>\n	<li>Keep this drug out of reach of children.</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>此藥可使人昏昏欲睡，服後如有此情形，不得駕駛或動用機械。</li>\n	<li>不適當使用此藥可引致肝臟中毒或肝臟嚴重損傷。切勿服食超過指定劑量。非經醫護人員指示，不可同時服用其他含有撲熱息痛的藥物。只要依照劑量及服法指示服用<strong>幸福傷風素是安全可靠的</strong>。</li>\n	<li>如屬以下情況，服用前應請示醫生：\n	<ul>\n		<li>正在接受醫生治療</li>\n		<li>正在服用醫生處方藥物</li>\n		<li>懷孕或哺乳期間</li>\n		<li>腎病或肝病患者</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>避免服用含有酒精飲料。</li>\n	<li>對本藥任何成分過敏者不可服用。</li>\n	<li>服用後若症狀持續或轉差，請立即尋求醫生意見。</li>\n	<li>請將此藥物放在兒童不能接觸到的地方。</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>此药可使人昏昏欲睡，服後如有此情形， 不得驾驶或动用机械。</li>\n	<li>不适当使用此药可引致肝脏中毒或肝脏严重损伤。切勿服食超过指定剂量。非经医护人员指示，不可同时服用其它含有扑热息痛的药物。只要依照剂量及服法指示服用<strong>幸福伤风素是安全可靠的</strong>。</li>\n	<li>如属以下情况，服用前应请示医生：\n	<ul>\n		<li>正在接受医生治疗</li>\n		<li>正在服用医生处方药物</li>\n		<li>怀孕或哺乳期间</li>\n		<li>肾病或肝病患者</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>避免服用含有酒精饮料。</li>\n	<li>对本药任何成分过敏者不可服用。</li>\n	<li>服用後若症状持续或转差，请立即寻求医生意见。</li>\n	<li>请将此药物放在儿童不能接触到的地方。</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>Store below 25&deg;C in a dry place in the original foil pack</li>\n	<li>Do not use if the foil pack is broken</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>儲存於25&deg;C以下乾爽地方及原本鋁箔包裝內</li>\n	<li>如鋁箔包裝破損，請勿使用</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>储存於25&deg;C以下乾爽地方及原本铝箔包装内</li>\n	<li>如铝箔包装破损，请勿使用</li>\n</ul>\n','For fast and effective relief of cold & flu symptoms:','有效迅速舒緩因普通感冒或流行性感冒症状：','有效迅速舒缓因普通感冒或流行性感冒症状：','','','','onset','2015-03-30 06:10:25','2017-03-16 17:31:38','0000-00-00 00:00:00',1,'Normal Series',0,'','','','','','',''),(2,'NoFroZic Lemon Mint','幸福樂喉適檸檬薄荷','幸福乐喉适柠檬薄荷','For effective relief of sore throat, mouth & throat infections','適用於喉痛 / 口腔及咽喉感染','适用於喉痛 / 口腔及咽喉感染','<ul>\n	<li>Fast and effective relief of sore throat and mouth &amp; throat infection