;</p>\n','<p><strong>Each tablet contains:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Paracetamol (Acetaminophen) 250mg</strong><br />\nPurpose: Relieves pain &amp; fever</p>\n\n<p><strong>Chlorpheniramine Maleate 2mg</strong><br />\nPurpose:&nbsp;Relieves allergic symptoms such as runny nose, sneezing, watery eyes and itchy eyes</p>\n\n<p><strong>Phenylephrine Hydrochloride 5mg</strong><br />\nPurpose: Relieves nasal congestion and eases breathing</p>\n\n<p><strong>Thiamine Hydrochloride (Vitamin B1) 3mg</strong><br />\nPurpose:&nbsp;Promotes carbohydrate metabolism and maintains normal functioning of the cardiovascular, nervous and digestive systems</p>\n\n<p><strong>Caffeine Anhydrous 30mg</strong><br />\nPurpose:&nbsp;Improves wakefulness and relieves tiredness caused by cold &amp; flu</p>\n','<p><strong>每片含量：</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>撲熱息痛 (對乙酰氨基酚) 250毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 止痛退燒，減輕頭痛、肌肉酸痛及咽喉痛等症狀</p>\n\n<p><strong>馬來酸氯苯那敏 2毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒緩流鼻水、打噴嚏、淚眼及眼部痕癢等過敏症狀</p>\n\n<p><strong>鹽酸去氧腎上腺素 5毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒緩鼻塞，令呼吸更為暢順</p>\n\n<p><strong>鹽酸硫胺 (維他命B1) 3毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 促進碳水化合物的新陳代謝，維持心臟血管、神經和消化系統的正常功能</p>\n\n<p><strong>無水咖啡因 30毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 有助提神及舒緩傷風感冒引起的疲倦</p>\n','<p><strong>每片含量：</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>扑热息痛 (对乙酰氨基酚) 250毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 止痛退烧，减轻头痛、肌肉酸痛及咽喉痛等症状</p>\n\n<p><strong>马来酸氯苯那敏 2毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒缓流鼻水、打喷嚏、泪眼及眼部痕痒等过敏症状</p>\n\n<p><strong>盐酸去氧肾上腺素 5毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒缓鼻塞，令呼吸更为畅顺</p>\n\n<p><strong>维生素B1 3毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 促进碳水化合物的新陈代谢，维持心脏血管、神经和消化系统的正常功能</p>\n\n<p><strong>无水咖啡因 30毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 有助提神及舒缓伤风感冒引起的疲倦</p>\n','<ul>\n	<li>Ask a doctor or a pharmacist before use if you are old aged, have heart disease, high blood pressure, thyroid disease, diabetes, enlargement of prostate gland or glaucoma.</li>\n	<li>Avoid taking if you are allergic to this product.</li>\n	<li>Do not take when there is a physical change of the product.</li>\n	<li>If you are on medication, consult a doctor or a pharmacist before taking this product.</li>\n	<li>To be taken with care if:\n	<ul>\n		<li>you have impaired liver and kidney function</li>\n		<li>you are pregnant or nursing baby</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>When taking this product, avoid\n	<ul>\n		<li>driving and operate machinery</li>\n		<li>alcoholic drinks or any alcohol containing drink when taking this product</li>\n		<li>taking other similar cold and flu medicine</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>If symptoms do not improve after taking 3 to 7 days. Consult a doctor or pharmacist.</li>\n	<li>If overdose or serious adverse effect appear, consult a doctor.</li>\n	<li>Keep this drug out of reach of children.</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>老年人、心臟病、高血壓、甲狀腺疾病、糖尿病、前列腺肥大等患者使用本品前請咨詢醫師或藥師。</li>\n	<li>對本藥任何成份過敏者禁用。</li>\n	<li>當本藥性狀發生改變時禁用。</li>\n	<li>如正在服用其他藥品，使用本品前請咨詢醫師或藥師。</li>\n	<li>以下情況慎用：\n	<ul>\n		<li>肝腎功能不全者</li>\n		<li>孕婦及哺乳期婦女</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>服用本品期間禁止：\n	<ul>\n		<li>駕駛或動用機械</li>\n		<li>飲酒或含有酒精的飲料</li>\n		<li>與其他解熱鎮痛藥同用，從而增加腎毒性的危險</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>本品不宜與氯霉素、巴比妥類、解痙藥、酚妥拉明、洋地黃苷類合用。</li>\n	<li>用藥3-7天，症狀未緩解，請咨詢醫師或藥師。</li>\n	<li>請將此藥品放在兒童不能接觸到的地方。</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>老年人、心脏病、高血压、甲状腺疾病、糖尿病、前列腺肥大等患者使用本品前请咨询医师或药师。</li>\n	<li>对本药任何成份过敏者禁用。</li>\n	<li>当本药性状发生改变时禁用。</li>\n	<li>如正在服用其他药品，使用本品前请咨询医师或药师。</li>\n	<li>以下情况慎用：\n	<ul>\n		<li>肝肾功能不全者</li>\n		<li>孕妇及哺乳期妇女</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>服用本品期间禁止：\n	<ul>\n		<li>驾驶或动用机械</li>\n		<li>饮酒或含有酒精的饮料</li>\n		<li>与其他解热镇痛药同用，从而增加肾毒性的危险</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>本品不宜与氯霉素、巴比妥类、解痉药、酚妥拉明、洋地黄苷类合用。</li>\n	<li>用药3-7天，症状未缓解，请咨询医师或药师。</li>\n	<li>请将此药品放在儿童不能接触到的地方。</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>Store below 25&deg;C in a dry place in the original foil pack</li>\n	<li>Do not use if the foil pack is broken</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>儲存於陰涼乾爽地方及原本鋁箔包裝內</li>\n	<li>如鋁箔包裝破損，請勿使用</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>储存于阴凉干爽地方及原本铝箔包装内</li>\n	<li>如铝箔包装破损，请勿使用</li>\n</ul>\n','Fast and effective relief of symptoms associated with common cold and flu:','有效迅速舒緩因普通感冒或流行性感冒引起的症状：','有效迅速舒缓因普通感冒或流行性感冒引起的症状：','','','','','2015-04-08 