/伤风感冒配方','<ul>\n	<li>Temporarily relief of cold &amp; flu or hay fever symptoms including minor aches and pains, sore throat, headache, runny nose, nasal congestion, fever, sneezing, itching eyes, nose or throat.</li>\n	<li>Fruit flavor chewable tablets,suitable for children 6-12 years.</li>\n	<li>Aspirin free - less likely to cause gastric discomfort.</li>\n	<li>Sugar free - no tooth decay.</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>舒緩因傷風感冒和花粉熱引起之症狀，包括輕微疼痛、喉嚨痛、頭痛、流鼻水、鼻塞、發燒、噴嚏、眼部、鼻腔或喉嚨痕癢等不適。</li>\n	<li>菓子味咀嚼片，專為6至12歲兒童而配製。</li>\n	<li>不含亞士匹靈，甚少引致腸胃不適。</li>\n	<li>不含糖份，不會引致蛀牙。</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>舒缓因伤风感冒和花粉热引起之症状，包括轻微疼痛、喉咙痛、头痛、流鼻水、鼻塞、发烧、喷嚏、眼部、鼻腔或喉咙痕痒等不适。</li>\n	<li>菓子味咀嚼片，专为6至12岁儿童而配制。</li>\n	<li>不含阿司匹林，甚少引致肠胃不适。</li>\n	<li>不含糖份，不会引致蛀牙。</li>\n</ul>\n','G9bHxEwInXtZMXOys47MbQJ5owiicgdD.png','','',3,10,'NDC 51467-006-01',0,'<ul>\n	<li>Available in packs of 24 chewable tablets</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>咀嚼片</li>\n	<li>24片裝</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>咀嚼片</li>\n	<li>24片装</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>Age:&nbsp;</strong>Children 6 to under 12 years<br />\n<strong>Dosage and Administration:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Chew tablets before swallowing</li>\n	<li>Four tablets every 4 hours</li>\n	<li>While symptoms persist, not to exceed 5 doses (twenty tablets) in 24 hours.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>OR&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>As directed by a doctor</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Age:&nbsp;</strong><strong>Children under 6 years</strong><br />\n<strong>Dosage and Administration:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Consult a doctor before use</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>歳數：</strong>6至12歲以下兒童<br />\n<strong>劑量服法</strong><strong>：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>吞嚥前咀嚼藥片</li>\n	<li>每4小時服用四片</li>\n	<li>如症狀持續，24小時內不超過5劑(二十片)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>或</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>遵照醫生指示服食</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>歳數：</strong>6歲以下兒童<br />\n<strong>劑量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>遵照醫生指示服食</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>歳数：</strong>6至12岁以下儿童<br />\n<strong>剂量服法</strong><strong>：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>吞咽前咀嚼药片</li>\n	<li>每4小时服用四片</li>\n	<li>如症状持续，24小时内不超过5剂(二十片)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>或</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>遵照医生指示服食</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>歳数：</strong>6岁以下儿童<br />\n<strong>剂量服法</strong><strong>：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>遵照医生指示服食</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>Each tablet contains:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Paracetamol (Acetaminophen) 80mg</strong><br />\nPurpose: Relieves pain &amp; fever</p>\n\n<p><strong>Chlorpheniramine Maleate 0.5mg</strong><br />\nPurpose:&nbsp;Relieves allergic symptoms such as runny nose, sneezing, watery eyes and itchy eyes</p>\n\n<p><strong>Phenylephrine Hydrochloride 1.25mg</strong><br />\nPurpose: Relieves nasal congestion and eases breathing</p>\n\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:none\">\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>每片含量：</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>撲熱息痛 (對乙酰氨基酚) 80毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 止痛退燒，減輕頭痛、肌肉酸痛及咽喉痛等症狀</p>\n\n<p><strong>馬來酸氯苯那敏 0.5毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒緩流鼻水、打噴嚏、淚眼及眼部痕癢等過敏症狀</p>\n\n<p><strong>鹽酸去氧腎上腺素 1.25毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒緩鼻塞，令呼吸更為暢順</p>\n\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:none\">\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>每片含量：</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>扑热息痛</strong><strong>&nbsp;(</strong><strong>对乙酰氨基酚</strong><strong>) 80</strong><strong>毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 止痛退烧，减轻头痛、肌肉酸痛及咽喉痛等症状</p>\n\n<p><strong>马来酸氯苯那敏</strong><strong>&nbsp;0.5</strong><strong>毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒缓流鼻水、打喷嚏、泪眼及眼部痕痒等过敏症状</p>\n\n<p><strong>盐酸脱氧肾上腺素</strong><strong>&nbsp;1.25</strong><strong>毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒缓鼻塞，令呼吸更为畅顺</p>\n\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:none\">\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>Liver warning: This product contains acetaminophen. Severe liver damage may occur if your child takes:\n	<ul>\n		<li>more than 5 doses in 24 hours, which the maximum daily amount for this product</li>\n		<li>with other drugs containing acetaminophen</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Do not use:\n	<ul>\n		<li>with any other drug containing acetaminophen (prescription or nonprescription). If you are not sure whether a drug contains acetaminophen, ask a doctor or pharmacist.</li>\n		<li>in a child who is taking a prescription monoamine oxidase inhibitor (MAOI) (certain drugs for depression, psychiatric or emotional conditions, or Parkinson&rsquo;s disease).</li>\n		<li>for 2 weeks after stopping the MAOI drug</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Ask a doctor before use if your child has:\n	<ul>\n		<li>liver disease</li>\n		<li>heart disease</li>\n		<li>high blood pressure</li>\n		<li>thyroid disease</li>\n		<li>diabetes</li>\n		<li>glaucoma</li>\n		<li>a breathing problem such as chronic bronchitis</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Ask a doctor or pharmacist before use if your child is:\n	<ul>\n		<li>taking the blood thinning drug warfarin</li>\n		<li>taking sedatives or tranquilizers</li>\n		<li>taking a prescription drug and you do not know if it contains a MAOI</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>When using this product:\n	<ul>\n		<li>do not exceed recommended dosage</li>\n		<li>may cause drowsiness (sedatives and tranquilizers may increase the drowsiness effect)</li>\n		<li>may cause excitability especially in children</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Stop use and ask a doctor if:\n	<ul>\n		<li>sore throat persists for more than 2 days</li>\n		<li>sore throat is severe</li>\n		<li>sore throat is accompanied or followed by: fever, headache, rash, nausea, vomoting</li>\n		<li>pain or nasal congestion gets worse or lasts more than 5 days</li>\n		<li>fever gets worse or lasts more than 3 days</li>\n		<li>redness or swelling is present</li>\n		<li>new symptoms occur</li>\n		<li>if nervousness, dizziness, or sleeplessness occur</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Do not give to children under 6 years of age unless directed by a doctor.</li>\n	<li>If pregnant or breast-feeding, ask a health professional before use.</li>\n	<li>Keep out of reach of children.</li>\n	<li>In case of overdose, get medical help or contact a Poison Control Center&nbsp;right away.&nbsp;Prompt medical attention is critical for adults as well as children even if you do not notice any signs or&nbsp;symptoms.</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>肝臟警告︰本產品含有對乙酰氨基酚。可導致肝臟嚴重損傷，如果您的孩子︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>在24小時內服用超過5劑，這是本產品的最大日用量</li>\n		<li>與其他含有對乙酰氨基酚的藥物一起服用</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>不能用於︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>與其他含有對乙酰氨基酚的藥物 (處方或非處方) 一起使用。如果您不確定某種藥物是否含有對乙酰氨基酚，請向醫生或藥劑師查詢。</li>\n		<li>如果孩子正在服用處方的單胺氧化酶抑制劑(MAOI) (用於治療抑鬱症、精神或情緒疾病或巴金森氏症的某些藥物)。</li>\n		<li>在停止MAOI藥物後達兩周</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>在使用前向醫生咨詢，如果使用者有︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>肝臟疾病</li>\n		<li>心臟病</li>\n		<li>高血壓</li>\n		<li>甲狀腺疾病</li>\n		<li>糖尿病</li>\n		<li>青光眼</li>\n		<li>慢性支氣管炎等呼吸疾病</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>在使用前向醫生或藥劑師咨詢，如果使用者正在︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>服用血液稀釋藥物殺鼠靈</li>\n		<li>服用安定或鎮靜藥物</li>\n		<li>服用處方藥物，而且不知道是否含有MAOI</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>在使用本產品時︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>切勿超過建議劑量</li>\n		<li>可能導致嗜睡 (安定藥物和鎮靜藥物可增加嗜睡作用)</li>\n		<li>可能導致興奮性，特別是對於兒童而言</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>停止使用並向醫生咨詢，如果︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>咽喉腫痛持續超過2天</li>\n		<li>咽喉腫痛變嚴重</li>\n		<li>咽喉腫痛伴隨以下症狀︰發燒、頭痛、皮疹、噁心或嘔吐</li>\n		<li>疼痛或鼻塞變嚴重或持續超過5天</li>\n		<li>發燒變嚴重或持續超過3天</li>\n		<li>出現紅腫</li>\n		<li>出現新症狀</li>\n		<li>出現緊張不安、頭暈或失眠症狀</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>除非醫生建議，切勿給6歲以下兒童服用。</li>\n	<li>放置在兒童取不到的地方。</li>\n	<li>如果服用過量，請立即送醫或聯絡毒物控制中心。無論是對於成人或是對於兒童而言，迅速的醫療處理都是至關重要的，即使您沒有發現任何徵兆或症狀也是如此。</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','<ul>\n	<li>肝脏警告︰本产品含有对乙酰氨基酚。可导致肝脏严重损伤，如果您的孩子︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>在24小时内服用超过5剂，这是本产品的最大日用量</li>\n		<li>与其他含有对乙酰氨基酚的药物一起服用</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>不能用于︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>与其他含有对乙酰氨基酚的药物 (处方或非处方) 一起使用。如果您不确定某种药物是否含有对乙酰氨基酚，请向医生或药剂师查询。</li>\n		<li>如果孩子正在服用处方的单胺氧化酶抑制剂(MAOI)&nbsp;(用于治疗抑郁症、精神或情绪疾病或巴金森氏症的某些药物)。</li>\n		<li>在停止MAOI药物后达两周</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>在使用前向医生咨询，如果使用者有︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>肝脏疾病</li>\n		<li>心脏病</li>\n		<li>高血压</li>\n		<li>甲状腺疾病</li>\n		<li>糖尿病</li>\n		<li>青光眼</li>\n		<li>慢性支气管炎等呼吸疾病</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>在使用前向医生或药剂师咨询，如果使用者正在︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>服用血液稀释药物杀鼠灵</li>\n		<li>服用安定或镇静药物</li>\n		<li>服用处方药物，而且不知道是否含有MAOI</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>在使用本产品时︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>切勿超过建议剂量</li>\n		<li>可能导致嗜睡 (安定药物和镇静药物可增加嗜睡作用)</li>\n		<li>可能导致兴奋性，特别是对于儿童而言</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>停止使用并向医生咨询，如果︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>咽喉肿痛持续超过2天</li>\n		<li>咽喉肿痛变严重</li>\n		<li>咽喉肿痛伴随以下症状︰发烧、头痛、皮疹、恶心或呕吐</li>\n		<li>疼痛或鼻塞变严重或持续超过5天</li>\n		<li>发烧变严重或持续超过3天</li>\n		<li>出现红肿</li>\n		<li>出现新症状</li>\n		<li>出现紧张不安、头晕或失眠症状</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>除非医生建议，切勿给6岁以下儿童服用。</li>\n	<li>放置在儿童取不到的地方。</li>\n	<li>如果服用过量，请立即送医或联络毒物控制中心。无论是对于成人或是对于儿童而言，迅速的医疗处理都是至关重要的，即使您没有发现任何征兆或症状也是如此。</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>Store between 15&deg;C to 30&deg;C (59&deg;F to 86&deg;F) in original foil pack</li>\n	<li>Please do not use if foil pack&nbsp;is broken</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>儲存於陰涼乾爽地方及原本鋁箔包裝內</li>\n	<li>如鋁箔包裝破損，請勿使用</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>储存于阴凉干爽地方及原本铝箔包装内</li>\n	<li>如铝箔包装破损，请勿使用</li>\n</ul>\n','Temporarily relief of cold & flu or hay fever symptoms:','舒緩傷風感冒和花粉熱症狀：','舒缓伤风感冒和花粉热症状：','','','','onset','2015-04-10 08:18:48','2017-02-09 22:53:21','0000-00-00 00:00:00',1,'Children Series',0,'','','','','','',''),(18,'CHILDREN\'S FORTOLIN','兒童幸福止痛退熱素','儿童幸福止痛退热素','For Age 3-12/Analgestic & antipyretic formula','3-12歲/止痛退熱配方','3-12岁/止痛退热配方','<ul>\n	<li>Fast and safe relief of fever and pain such as toothache, headache and sore throat.</li>\n	<li>Ingredient widely used by medical professionals.</li>\n	<li>Fruit flavor chewable tablets,suitable for children.</li>\n	<li>Aspirin free - less likely to cause gastric discomfort.</li>\n	<li>Sugar free - no tooth decay.</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>迅速舒緩發燒及各種痛症如牙痛、頭痛及喉嚨痛。</li>\n	<li>所含成份最為醫學界選用。</li>\n	<li>菓子味咀嚼片，專為兒童而配製。</li>\n	<li>不含亞士匹靈，甚少引致腸胃不適。</li>\n	<li>不含糖份，不會引致蛀牙。</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>迅速舒缓发烧及各种痛症如牙痛、头痛及喉咙痛。</li>\n	<li>所含成份最为医学界选用。</li>\n	<li>菓子味咀嚼片，专为儿童而配制。</li>\n	<li>不含阿司匹林，甚少引致肠胃不适。</li>\n	<li>不含糖份，不会引致蛀牙。</li>\n</ul>\n','JUZKc7gVzdXdJGxO0cPRDoGDMSmSxrqt.png','','',1,9,'HK-48963',0,'<ul>\n	<li>Available in pack of 16 chewable tablets</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>咀嚼片</li>\n	<li>16片裝</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>咀嚼片</li>\n	<li>16片装</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>Age: </strong>Children under 3 years &nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n<strong>Dosage and Administration: </strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Use only as directed by physician</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Age:</strong> Children 3 years<br />\n<strong>Dosage and Administration:</strong>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>One tablet every 4 to 6 hours</li>\n	<li>Not to exceed four tablets in 24 hours</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Age: </strong>Children 4 to 6 years &nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n<strong>Dosage and Administration:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Two tablets every 4 to 6 hours</li>\n	<li>Not to exceed eight tablets in 24 hours</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Age: </strong>Children 7 to 9 years &nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n<strong>Dosage and Administration:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Three tablets every 4 to 6 hours</li>\n	<li>Not to exceed twelve tablets in 24 hours</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Age:</strong> Children 10 to 12 years &nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n<strong>Dosage and Administration:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Four tablets every 4 to 6 hours</li>\n	<li>Not to exceed sixteen tablets in 24 hours</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Remarks：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>Chew tablets before swallowing.</strong></li>\n	<li><strong>Take each dose with plenty of water.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>歳數：</strong>3歲以下兒童<br />\n<strong>劑量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>遵照醫生指示才可服用</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>歳數：</strong>3歲兒童<br />\n<strong>劑量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每次服一片，每4至6小時服1次</li>\n	<li>24小時內不可服用超過四片</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>歳數：</strong>4至6歲兒童<br />\n<strong>劑量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每次服兩片，每4至6小時服1次</li>\n	<li>24小時內不可服用超過八片</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>歳數：</strong>7至9歲兒童<br />\n<strong>劑量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每次服三片，每4至6小時服1次</li>\n	<li>24小時內不可服用超過十二片</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>歳數：</strong>10至12歲兒童<br />\n<strong>劑量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每次服四片，每4至6小時服1次</li>\n	<li>24小時內不可服用超過十六片</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>備註：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>藥片放入口中完全嚼碎後再吞服</strong></li>\n	<li><strong>服用時宜多飲開水。</strong></li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>歳数：</strong>3岁以下儿童<br />\n<strong>剂量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>遵照医生指示才可服用</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>歳数：</strong>3岁儿童<br />\n<stron