舒緩鼻塞，令呼吸更為暢順</p>\n\n<p><strong>氫溴酸美沙芬</strong><strong> 13.5毫克&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><br />\n用途：抑制咳嗽</p>\n','<p><strong>每片含量：</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>扑热息痛</strong><strong> (对乙酰氨基酚) 325毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 止痛退烧，减轻头痛、肌肉酸痛及咽喉痛等症状</p>\n\n<p><strong>马来酸氯苯那敏</strong><strong> 2毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒缓流鼻水、打喷嚏、泪眼及眼部痕痒等过敏症状</p>\n\n<p><strong>盐酸去氧肾上腺素</strong><strong> 5毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒缓鼻塞，令呼吸更为畅顺</p>\n\n<p><strong>氢溴酸美沙芬</strong>&nbsp;<strong>13.5毫克</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n用途：抑制咳嗽</p>\n','<ul>\n	<li>Liver warning: This product contains acetaminophen. Severe liver damage may occur if:\n	<ul>\n		<li>adult takes more than twelve tablets in 24 hours, which the maximum daily amount for this product</li>\n		<li>child takes more than five tablets in 24 hours</li>\n		<li>taken with other drugs containing acetaminophen</li>\n		<li>adult has 3 or more alcoholic drinks everyday while using this product</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Do not use:\n	<ul>\n		<li>with any other drug containing acetaminophen (prescription or nonprescription). If you are not sure whether a drug contains acetaminophen, ask a doctor or pharmacist.</li>\n		<li>if you are now taking a prescription monoamine oxidase inhibitor (MAOI) (certain drugs for depression, psychiatric or emotional conditions, or Parkinson&rsquo;s disease). If you do not know whether a prescription drug contains an MAOI, ask a doctor or pharmacist.</li>\n		<li>for 2 weeks after stopping the MAOI drug</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Ask a doctor before use if the user has:\n	<ul>\n		<li>liver disease</li>\n		<li>heart disease</li>\n		<li>high blood pressure</li>\n		<li>thyroid disease</li>\n		<li>diabetes</li>\n		<li>glaucoma</li>\n		<li>difficulty in urination due to enlargement of the prostate gland</li>\n		<li>high fever</li>\n		<li>breathing problem such as emphysema or chronic bronchitis</li>\n		<li>persistent cough</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Ask a doctor or pharmacist before use if the user is:\n	<ul>\n		<li>taking the blood thinning drug warfarin</li>\n		<li>taking sedatives or tranquilizers</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>When using this product:\n	<ul>\n		<li>do not exceed recommended dosage</li>\n		<li>may cause excitability especially in children</li>\n		<li>do not drive or operate machinery</li>\n		<li>avoid alcoholic beverages</li>\n		<li>may cause drowsiness;&nbsp;alcohol, sedatives, and tranquilizers may increase the drowsiness effect</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Stop use and ask a doctor if:\n	<ul>\n		<li>Pain, cough or nasal congestion gets worse or lasts more than 5 days (children) or 7 days (adults)</li>\n		<li>sore throat persists for more than 2 days</li>\n		<li>nasal congestion is accompanied by fever</li>\n		<li>nervousness, dizziness, or sleeplessness occur</li>\n		<li>any of the following occurs (these could be signs of a serious condition):&nbsp;fever gets worse or lasts more than 3 days; severe sore throat;&nbsp;sore throat is accompanied or followed by fever, headache, rash, nausea or vomiting; redness or swelling is present; new symptoms occur; cough persists for more than 1 week, tends to recur, or is accompanied by fever, rash, or persistent headache.</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Do not give to children under 6 years of age unless directed by a doctor.</li>\n	<li>If pregnant or breast-feeding, ask a health professional before use.</li>\n	<li>Keep out of reach of children.</li>\n	<li>In case of overdose, get medical help or contact a Poison Control Center&nbsp;right away.&nbsp;Prompt medical attention is critical for adults as well as children even if you do not notice any signs or&nbsp;symptoms.</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>肝臟警告︰本產品含有對乙酰氨基酚。可導致肝臟嚴重損傷，如果︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>成人在24小時內服用超過十二片，這是本產品的最大日用量</li>\n		<li>兒童在24小時內服用超過五片</li>\n		<li>與其他含有對乙酰氨基酚的藥物一起服用</li>\n		<li>成人在使用本產品時每日飲用3次以上的含酒精飲料</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>不能用於︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>與其他含有對乙酰氨基酚的藥物 (處方或非處方) 一起使用。如果您不確定某種藥物是否含有對乙酰氨基酚，請向醫生或藥劑師查詢。</li>\n		<li>如果您正在服用處方的單胺氧化酶抑制劑(MAOI) (用於治療抑鬱症、精神或情緒疾病或巴金森氏症的某些藥物)。如果您不確定某種處方藥物是否含有MAOI，請向醫生或藥劑師咨詢。</li>\n		<li>在停止MAOI藥物後達兩周</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>在使用前向醫生咨詢，如果使用者有︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>肝臟疾病</li>\n		<li>心臟病</li>\n		<li>高血壓</li>\n		<li>甲狀腺疾病</li>\n		<li>糖尿病</li>\n		<li>因前列腺肥大引起的排尿困難</li>\n		<li>青光眼</li>\n		<li>高燒</li>\n		<li>肺氣腫或慢性支氣管炎等呼吸疾病</li>\n		<li>持續咳嗽</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>在使用前向醫生或藥劑師咨詢，如果使用者正在︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>服用血液稀釋藥物殺鼠靈</li>\n		<li>服用安定或鎮靜藥物</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>在使用本產品時︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>切勿超過建議劑量</li>\n		<li>可能導致興奮性，特別是對於兒童而言</li>\n		<li>在開車或操作機器時要謹慎服用</li>\n		<li>避免含酒精飲料</li>\n		<li>可能導致嗜睡；酒精、安定藥物和鎮靜藥物可增加嗜睡作用</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>停止使用並向醫生咨詢，如果︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>疼痛或鼻塞變嚴重或持續超過5天(兒童)或7天(成人)</li>\n		<li>咽喉腫痛持續超過2天</li>\n		<li>鼻塞伴隨發燒</li>\n		<li>出現緊張不安、頭暈或失眠症狀</li>\n		<li>出現任何以下症狀(這些可能是嚴重疾病的徵兆)︰發燒愈加嚴重或持續超過3天; 嚴重喉嚨腫痛; 咽喉腫痛伴隨發燒、頭痛、皮疹、噁心或嘔吐; 有紅腫症狀; 出現新症狀; 咳嗽持續超過1週，可能會復發，或伴隨發燒、皮疹或持續頭痛。</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>除非醫生建議，切勿給6歲以下兒童服用。</li>\n	<li>如果懷孕或正在哺乳，請在使用前向醫療專業人員咨詢。</li>\n	<li>放置在兒童取不到的地方。</li>\n	<li>如果服用過量，請立即送醫或聯絡毒物控制中心。無論是對於成人或是對於兒童而言，迅速的醫療處理都是至關重要的，即使您沒有發現任何徵兆或症狀也是如此。</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','<ul>\n	<li>肝脏警告︰本产品含有对乙酰氨基酚。可导致肝脏严重损伤，如果︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>成人在24小时内服用超过十二片，这是本产品的最大日用量</li>\n		<li>儿童在24小时内服用超过五片</li>\n		<li>与其他含有对乙酰氨基酚的药物一起服用</li>\n		<li>成人在使用本产品时每日饮用3次以上的含酒精饮料</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>不能用于︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>与其他含有对乙酰氨基酚的药物 (处方或非处方) 一起使用。如果您不确定某种药物是否含有对乙酰氨基酚，请向医生或药剂师查询。</li>\n		<li>如果您正在服用处方的单胺氧化酶抑制剂(MAOI) (用于治疗抑郁症、精神或情绪疾病或巴金森氏症的某些药物)。如果您不确定某种处方药物是否含有MAOI，请向医生或药剂师咨询。</li>\n		<li>在停止MAOI药物后达两周</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>在使用前向医生咨询，如果使用者有︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>肝脏疾病</li>\n		<li>心脏病</li>\n		<li>高血压</li>\n		<li>甲状腺疾病</li>\n		<li>糖尿病</li>\n		<li>因前列腺肥大引起的排尿困难</li>\n		<li>青光眼</li>\n		<li>高烧</li>\n		<li>肺气肿或慢性支气管炎等呼吸疾病</li>\n		<li>持续咳嗽</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>在使用前向医生或药剂师咨询，如果使用者正在︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>服用血液稀释药物杀鼠灵</li>\n		<li>服用安定或镇静药物</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>在使用本产品时︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>切勿超过建议剂量</li>\n		<li>可能导致兴奋性，特别是对于儿童而言</li>\n		<li>在开车或操作机器时要谨慎服用</li>\n		<li>避免含酒精饮料</li>\n		<li>可能导致嗜睡；酒精、安定药物和镇静药物可增加嗜睡作用</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>停止使用并向医生咨询，如果︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>疼痛或鼻塞变严重或持续超过5天(儿童)或7天(成人)</li>\n		<li>咽喉肿痛持续超过2天</li>\n		<li>鼻塞伴随发烧</li>\n		<li>出现紧张不安、头晕或失眠症状</li>\n		<li>出现任何以下症状(这些可能是严重疾病的征兆)︰发烧愈加严重或持续超过3天; 严重喉咙肿痛; 咽喉肿痛伴随发烧、头痛、皮疹、恶心或呕吐; 有红肿症状; 出现新症状; 咳嗽持续超过1周，可能会复发，或伴随发烧、皮疹或持续头痛。</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>除非医生建议，切勿给6岁以下儿童服用。</li>\n	<li>如果怀孕或正在哺乳，请在使用前向医疗专业人员咨询。</li>\n	<li>放置在儿童取不到的地方。</li>\n	<li>如果服用过量，请立即送医或联络毒物控制中心。无论是对于成人或是对于儿童而言，迅速的医疗处理都是至关重要的，即使您没有发现任何征兆或症状也是如此。</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','<ul>\n	<li>Store between 15&deg;C to 30&deg;C (59&deg;F to 86&deg;F) in original foil pack</li>\n	<li>Please do not use if foil pack is broken</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>儲存於陰涼乾爽地方及原本鋁箔包裝內</li>\n	<li>如鋁箔包裝破損，請勿使用</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>储存于阴凉干爽地方及原本铝箔包装内</li>\n	<li>如铝箔包装破损，请勿使用</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','Temporarily relief of cold & flu or hay fever symptoms:','舒緩傷風感冒和花粉熱症狀：','舒缓伤风感冒和花粉热症状：','','','','onset','2015-04-30 07:20:16','2017-01-26 22:59:50','0000-00-00 00:00:00',1,'',0,'','','','','','',''),(21,'COLTALIN-DM','幸福傷風咳素-DM','幸福伤风咳素-DM','Special Quick Recovery Forumla for Colds, Flu and Allergy','止咳除痰/傷風感冒綜合配方','止咳除痰/伤风感冒综合配方','<ul>\n	<li>Fast and effective relief of cold &amp; flu symptoms including sneezing, running nose, fever, nasal congestion, muscular pains and headache.</li>\n	<li>Aspirin free -- unlikely to cause gastric which between irritation and commonly occurs with aspirin.</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>迅速有效消除因傷風感冒引起的不適，包括痰多咳嗽、噴嚏、流鼻水、鼻塞、頭痛、發燒及肌肉酸痛等。</li>\n	<li>不含亞士匹靈，故無一般服食亞士匹靈可能會導致的腸胃刺激。</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>迅速有效消除因伤风感冒引起的不适，包括痰多咳嗽、喷嚏、流鼻水、鼻塞、头痛、发烧及肌肉酸痛等。</li>\n	<li>不含亚士匹灵，故无一般服食亚士匹灵可能会导致的肠胃刺激。</li>\n</ul>\n','jzvXFeZptrFV3kbpFZEIIuWdwb8k2pXK.png','','',3,11,'',0,'<p>Available in packs of 24 tablets</p>\n','<ul>\n	<li>藥片</li>\n	<li>24片裝</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>药片</li>\n	<li>24片装</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>Age:</strong> Adults &amp; children over 12 years&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n<strong>Dosage and Administration:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>2 tablets every 4 hours</li>\n	<li>while symptoms persist, not to exceed 6 doses (12 tablets) in 24 hours</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>or</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>as directed by a doctor</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Age:</strong> Children 6 - 12 years&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n<strong>Dosage and Administration:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>1 tablets every 4 hours</li>\n	<li>while symptoms persist, not to exceed 5 doses (5 tablets) in 24 hours</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>or</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>as directed by a doctor</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Age:</strong> Children under 6 years&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n<strong>Dosage and Administration:</strong> Consult a doctor</p>\n\n<p><strong>Remarks：Copious intake of water afterwards is advisable</strong></p>\n','<p><strong>歲數：</strong>成人及12歲以上兒童&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n<strong>劑量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每4小時服2片</li>\n	<li>24小時內不得服用超過12片</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>或</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>遵照醫生指示服食</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>歲數：</strong>6至12歲兒童<br />\n<strong>劑量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每4小時服1片</li>\n	<li>24小時內不得服用超過5片</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>或</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>遵照醫生指示服食</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>歲數：</strong>6歲以下兒童&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n<strong>劑量服法：</strong>遵照醫生指示服食</p>\n\n<p><strong>備註：服後宜多飲開水。</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n','<p><strong>岁数：</strong>成人及12岁以上儿童<br />\n<strong>剂量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每4小时服2片</li>\n	<li>24小时内不得服用超过12片</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>或</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>遵照医生指示服食</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>岁数：</strong>6至12岁儿童<br />\n<strong>剂量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每4小时服1片</li>\n	<li>24小时内不得服用超过5片</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>或</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>遵照医生指示服食</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>岁数：</strong>6岁以下儿童<br />\n<strong>剂量服法：</strong>遵照医生指示服食</p>\n\n<p><strong>备注：服后宜多饮开水。</strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','<p><strong>Each tablet contains: Acetaminophen (Paracetamol) 325mg&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><br />\nPurposes: Pain reliever &amp; fever reducer</p>\n\n<p><strong>Each tablet contains: Chlorpheniramine Maleate 2mg&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><br />\nPurposes: Antihistamine</p>\n\n<p><strong>Each tablet contains: Phenylephrine Hydrochloride 5mg&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><br />\nPurposes: Nasal decongestant</p>\n','<p><strong>每片含量：撲熱息痛(對乙酰氨基酚/醋氨酚)325毫克</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n用途：止痛、退燒</p>\n\n<p><strong>每片含量：馬來酸氯苯那敏(撲爾敏)2毫克&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n用途：抗過敏</p>\n\n<p><strong>每片含量：氫溴酸美沙芬10毫克&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n用途：鎮咳</p>\n\n<p><strong>每片含</strong>量：鹽酸去氧腎上腺素(鹽酸新福林)5毫克&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n用途：緩解鼻腔充血</p>\n','<p><strong>每片含量：扑热息痛(对乙酰氨基酚/醋氨酚)325毫克</strong><br />\n用途：止痛、退烧</p>\n\n<p><strong>每片含量：马来酸氯苯那敏(扑尔敏)2毫克</strong><br />\n用途：抗过敏</p>\n\n<p><strong>每片含量：氢溴酸美沙芬10毫克</strong><br />\n用途：镇咳</p>\n\n<p><strong>每片含量：盐酸去氧肾上腺素(盐酸新福林)5毫克</strong><br />\n用途：缓解鼻腔充血</p>\n','<ul>\n	<li><strong>COLTALIN TABLET is safe </strong>and reliable if &#39;Dosage and Administration&#39; is observed. Do not exceed the stated dose.</li>\n	<li>This drug may cause :\n	<ul>\n		<li>drowsiness. If affected, do not drive or operate machinery.</li>\n		<li>excitability, especially in children.</li>\n		<li>you are pregnant or are nursing baby</li>\n		<li>you have kidney or liver disease.</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Consult your doctor before use if :\n	<ul>\n		<li>you are pregnant or are nursing baby</li>\n		<li>you have heart disease, high blood pressure, thyroid disease, diabetes, glaucoma, a breathing problem such as emphysema or chronic bronchitis or difficulty in urination due to enlargement of the prostate gland</li>\n		<li>you are taking sedatives or tranquilizers</li>\n		<li>you do not know if your prescription drug contains MAOI</li>\n		<li>you consume 3 or more alcoholic drinks every day</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Stop using this drug and consult a doctor if:\n	<ul>\n		<li>symptoms do not improve</li>\n		<li>symptoms are accompanied by fever that lasts for more than 3 days</li>\n		<li>you have nervousness, dizziness, sleeplessness, new symptoms, severe sore throat, or sore throat which lasts more than 2 days</li>\n		<li>symptoms are accompanied or followed by: fever, headache, rash, nausea or vomiting</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Do not use with other products containing Acetaminophen (Paracetamol). It is dangerous to overdose</li>\n	<li>Avoid alcoholic drink. Alcohol, sedatives, and tranquilizers may increase the drowsiness effect</li>\n	<li>Do not use for more than 10 days for adults or 5 days for children</li>\n	<li>Keep this drug out of the reach of children</li>\n	<li>In case of overdose, get medical help or contact a Poison Control Center right away</li>\n</ul>\n','<p>依照劑量服法指示服用<strong>幸福傷風咳素</strong>是非常安全可靠的，切勿服用超過指定劑量<br />\n服用此藥物可能會出現以下情況:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>睡意；如有此情形，不可駕駛或操作機械</li>\n	<li>引起興奮，尤其是對兒童</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>如屬以下情況，服用前應請示醫生 :</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>懷孕或哺乳期間</li>\n	<li>患有青光眼、心臟病、高血壓、糖尿病、甲狀腺病、高熱、因抽煙、氣喘或肺氣腫引起的持續性或慢性咳嗽、咳嗽多痰、肺氣腫或慢性支氣管炎引起的呼吸問題、或因前列腺脹大引起排尿困難</li>\n	<li>服用安眠藥或鎮定劑期間</li>\n	<li>你不知道你的處方藥物是否包含單胺氧化酶抑制劑(MAOI)</li>\n	<li>每日飲用3杯或以上酒精飲品</li>\n	<li>咳嗽持續超過1星期或伴隨發高燒</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>如出現下列症狀，請停止服用本藥物並請示醫生:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>症狀不改善</li>\n	<li>持續伴有發燒3天以上</li>\n	<li>出現新的症狀、咳嗽持續7天以上、咳嗽容易復發、咳嗽伴有皮疹、頭痛不止、咽喉痛持續2天以上、咽喉痛伴有或隨後出現發熱、頭痛、皮疹、噁心、嘔吐、神經緊張、頭暈或失眠</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>不可同期服用其他含撲熱息痛(乙酰氨基酚)成份的藥物，以免因過量服用造成危險<br />\n避免服用含有酒精飲料；酒、安眠藥或鎮定劑會加強睡意<br />\n成人不得服食超過10天；兒童不得超過5天<br />\n請將此藥物放置在兒童不能拿取的地方<br />\n如不慎服用過量，應立即與醫生或毒物控制中心(Poison Control Center)聯絡</p>\n','<p>依照剂量服法指示服用<strong>幸福伤风咳素</strong>是非常安全可靠的，切勿服用超过指定剂量<br />\n服用此药物可能会出现以下情况:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>睡意；如有此情形，不可驾驶或操作机械</li>\n	<li>引起兴奋，尤其是对儿童</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>如属以下情况，服用前应请示医生 :</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>怀孕或哺乳期间</li>\n	<li>患有青光眼、心脏病、高血压、糖尿病、甲状腺病、高热、因抽烟、气喘或肺气肿引起的持续性或慢性咳嗽、咳嗽多痰、肺气肿或慢性支气管炎引起的呼吸问题、或因前列腺胀大引起排尿困难</li>\n	<li>服用安眠药或镇定剂期间</li>\n	<li>你不知道你的处方药物是否包含单胺氧化酶抑制剂(MAOI)</li>\n	<li>每日饮用3杯或以上酒精饮品</li>\n	<li>咳嗽持续超过1星期或伴随发高烧</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>如出现下列症状，请停止服用本药物并请示医生:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>症状不改善</li>\n	<li>持续伴有发烧3天以上</li>\n	<li>出现新的症状、咳嗽持续7天以上、咳嗽容易复发、咳嗽伴有皮疹、头痛不止、咽喉痛持续2天以上、咽喉痛伴有或随后出现发热、头痛、皮疹、恶心、呕吐、神经紧张、头晕或失眠</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>不可同期服用其他含扑热息痛(乙酰氨基酚)成份的药物，以免因过量服用造成危险<br />\n避免服用含有酒精饮料；酒、​​安眠药或镇定剂会加强睡意<br />\n成人不得服食超过10天；儿童不得超过5天<br />\n请将此药物放置在儿童不能拿取的地方<br />\n如不慎服用过量，应立即与医生或毒物控制中心(Poison Control Center)联络</p>\n','<ul>\n	<li>Store between 15&deg;C to 30&deg;C (59&deg;F to 86&deg;F) in original pack</li>\n	<li>Please do not use if package is broken</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>儲存於陰涼乾爽地方及原本鋁箔包裝內</li>\n	<li>如包裝有破損，請勿使用</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>储存于阴凉干爽地方及原本铝箔包装内</li>\n	<li>如包装有破损，请勿使用</li>\n</ul>\n','For fast and effective relief of cold & flu symptoms:','有效迅速消除傷風感冒及咳嗽症狀：','有效迅速消除伤风感冒及咳嗽症状：','','','','onset','2015-04-30 07:44:24','2015-10-06 04:41:42','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,'',0,'','','','','','',''),(22,'COLTALIN','幸福傷風素','幸福伤风素','Recovery forumla for colds, flu and allergy','收鼻水/抗過敏/傷風感冒配方','收鼻水/抗过敏/伤风感冒配方','<ul>\n	<li>Fast and effective relief of symptoms of the common cold, fever, headache, mild to moderate aches and pains, sneezing and runny nose due to common cold or allergy, and nasal congestion.</li>\n	<li>Aspirin free - less likely to cause gastric discomfort.</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>有效迅速舒緩感冒症狀、發燒、頭痛、輕微至中度疼痛、由感冒或過敏引起的打噴嚏及流鼻水，以及鼻塞。</li>\n	<li>不含亞士匹靈，甚少引致腸胃不適。</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>有效迅速舒缓感冒症状、发烧、头痛、轻微至中度疼痛、由感冒或过敏引起的打喷嚏及流鼻水，以及鼻塞。</li>\n	<li>不含阿司匹林，甚少引致肠胃不适。</li>\n</ul>\n','WPNocIEPWlg9JPDg7cayuST9ixUqgBh8.png','','',3,11,'',30,'<ul>\n	<li>Available in packs of 24 tablets</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>藥片</li>\n	<li>24片裝</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>药片</li>\n	<li>24片装</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>Age:</strong> Adults &amp; children 12 years and older &nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n<strong>Dosage and Administration:</strong>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Two tablets every 4 hours</li>\n	<li>Not to exceed eight tablets in 24 hours</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>歲數：</strong>成人及12歲或以上兒童<br />\n<strong>劑量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每4小時服用兩片</li>\n	<li>24小時內不得服用超過八片</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>岁数：</strong>成人及12岁或以上儿童<br />\n<strong>剂量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每4小时服用两片</li>\n	<li>24小时内不得服用超过八片</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>Each tablet contains:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Paracetamol (Acetaminophen) 325mg</strong><br />\nPurpose: Relieves pain &amp; fever</p>\n\n<p><strong>Chlorpheniramine Maleate 2mg</strong><br />\nPurpose:&nbsp;Relieves allergic symptoms such as runny nose, sneezing, watery eyes and itchy eyes</p>\n\n<p><strong>Phenylephrine Hydrochloride 5mg</strong><br />\nPurpose: Relieves nasal congestion and eases breathing</p>\n','<p><strong>每片含量：</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>撲熱息痛 (對乙酰氨基酚) 325毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 止痛退燒，減輕頭痛、肌肉酸痛及咽喉痛等症狀</p>\n\n<p><strong>馬來酸氯苯那敏 2毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒緩流鼻水、打噴嚏、淚眼及眼部痕癢等過敏症狀</p>\n\n<p><strong>鹽酸去氧腎上腺素 5毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒緩鼻塞，令呼吸更為暢順</p>\n','<p><strong>每片含量：</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>扑热息痛 (对乙酰氨基酚) 325毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 止痛退烧，减轻头痛、肌肉酸痛及咽喉痛等症状</p>\n\n<p><strong>马来酸氯苯那敏 2毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒缓流鼻水、打喷嚏、泪眼及眼部痕痒等过敏症状</p>\n\n<p><strong>盐酸去氧肾上腺素 5毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒缓鼻塞，令呼吸更为畅顺</p>\n','<ul>\n	<li><strong>KEEP OUT OF THE REACH OF CHILDREN.</strong></li>\n	<li>This package contains enough drug to seriously harm a child.</li>\n	<li>Read the complete label prior to use and follow all label instructions.</li>\n	<li><strong>ADULT USE ONLY. DO NOT</strong> take more than the recommended dose unless advised by your doctor. Use the smallest effective dose. Taking more than the maximum daily dose may cause drowsiness, excitability and <strong>severe or possibly fatal liver damage</strong>.</li>\n	<li><strong>DO NOT USE</strong> with other drugs containing <strong>Acetaminophen</strong>, or any other cough and cold medications since harm may occur, unless recommended by a doctor.</li>\n	<li><strong>DO NOT USE</strong> if you are allergic to any of the ingredients. Discontinue use if allergic reactions such as wheezing, rash or itching develop.</li>\n	<li>May cause drowsiness or excitability. <strong>DO NOT USE</strong> when you are engaged in activities requiring mental alertness.</li>\n	<li>Consult a doctor if symptoms worsen, last for more than 5 days, or fever lasts more than 3 days, or are accompanied by a high fever (&gt;38&deg;C) or the production of thick yellow/green phlegm.</li>\n	<li>Ask a doctor or a pharmacist before use if you:\n	<ul>\n		<li>are elderly;</li>\n		<li>are pregnant or breastfeeding;</li>\n		<li>have chronic alcoholism;</li>\n		<li>have a serious liver or kidney disease, chronic lung disease, heart or thyroid disease, high blood pressure, diabetes, difficulty in urination or glaucoma;</li>\n		<li>use any other medications including natural health products, prescription drugs, nonprescription drugs, salicylates or other pain and fever relief medications (nonsteroidal anti-inflammatory drugs (NSAIDS)).</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Side effects may include: allergic reaction, breathing difficulties, convulsions, drowsiness, hallucinations, and rapid heart rate.</li>\n	<li><strong>In case of overdose:</strong> Call a Poison Control Centre or doctor immediately, even if you do not notice any signs or symptoms. Within the first 24 hours you may experience increased sweating, nausea, vomiting, stomach pain, and loss of appetite.</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li><strong>請將此藥物放在兒童不能接觸到的地方。</strong></li>\n	<li>服用本藥前請先閱讀本標簽，並跟從指示服用本藥。</li>\n	<li><strong>只供成人及</strong><strong>12</strong><strong>歲或以上兒童服用。</strong>除非醫生建議，<strong>切勿</strong>服食超過建議劑量。服用最少有效劑量。服用超過每日最高劑量可能引致嗜睡、興奮性、<strong>嚴重甚至可能致命的肝臟損傷</strong>。</li>\n	<li>除非醫生建議，<strong>不可</strong>同時服用其他含有<strong>撲熱息痛</strong>的藥物，或其他傷風感冒和咳嗽藥物。</li>\n	<li>對本藥任何成分過敏者<strong>不可服用</strong>。如服後出現喘氣、紅腫或痕癢，必須停止服用本藥。</li>\n	<li>此藥可使人昏昏欲睡或興奮。如需要進行任何保持警覺的活動，<strong>不</strong><strong>可服用</strong>本藥。</li>\n	<li>服用後若症狀轉差、持續超過5天、發燒持續超過3天、伴隨高燒 (&gt;38&deg;C)或出現呈黃/綠色的濃痰，請立即尋求醫生意見。</li>\n	<li>如屬以下情況，服用前應請示醫生或藥劑師：\n	<ul>\n		<li>長者</li>\n		<li>懷孕或哺乳期間</li>\n		<li>長期飲酒</li>\n		<li>患有嚴重肝病或腎病、長期肝病、心臟或甲狀腺疾病、高血壓、糖尿病、排尿困難或青光眼</li>\n		<li>正在服食其他藥物包括天然保健產品、處方藥物、非處方藥物、水楊酸或其他止痛退熱藥物(非類固醇消炎止痛藥, NSAIDS)。</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>本藥可能引致以下不良反應︰過敏反應、呼吸困難、抽搐、昏昏欲睡、幻覺和心率加快。</li>\n	<li><strong>如果服用過量</strong>，即使沒有出現任何迹像或症狀，亦必須立即聯絡毒物管制中心 (Poison Control Centre) 或醫生。服用過量後首24小時可能會增加流汗、噁心、嘔吐、胃痛和食慾不振。</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li><strong>请将此药物放在儿童不能接触到的地方。</strong></li>\n	<li>服用本药前请先阅读本标签，并跟从指示服用本药。</li>\n	<li><strong>只供成人及12岁或以上儿童服用。</strong>除非医生建议，<strong>切勿</strong>服食超过建议剂量。服用最少有效剂量。服用超过每日最高剂量可能引致嗜睡、兴奋性、<strong>严重甚至可能致命的肝脏损伤</strong>。</li>\n	<li>除非医生建议，<strong>不可</strong>同时服用其他含有<strong>扑热息痛</strong>的药物，或其他伤风感冒和咳嗽药物。</li>\n	<li>对本药任何成分过敏者<strong>不可服用</strong>。如服后出现喘气、红肿或痕痒，必须停止服用本药。</li>\n	<li>此药可使人昏昏欲睡或兴奋。如需要进行任何保持警觉的活动，<strong>不可服用</strong>本药。</li>\n	<li>服用后若症状转差、持续超过5天、发烧持续超过3天、伴随高烧(&gt;38&deg;C)或出现呈黄/绿色的浓痰，请立即寻求医生意见。</li>\n	<li>如属以下情况，服用前应请示医生或药剂师：\n	<ul>\n		<li>长者</li>\n		<li>怀孕或哺乳期间</li>\n		<li>长期饮酒</li>\n		<li>患有严重肝病或肾病、长期肝病、心脏或甲状腺疾病、高血压、糖尿病、排尿困难或青光眼</li>\n		<li>正在服食其他药物包括天然保健产品、处方药物、非处方药物、水杨酸或其他止痛退热药物(非类固醇消炎止痛药, NSAIDS)。</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>本药可能引致以下不良反应︰过敏反应、呼吸困难、抽搐、昏昏欲睡、幻觉和心率加快。</li>\n	<li><strong>如果服用过量</strong>，即使没有出现任何迹像或症状，亦必须立即联络毒物管制中心(Poison Control Centre) 或医生。服用过量后首24小时可能会增加流汗、恶心、呕吐、胃痛和食欲不振。</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>Store between 15&deg;C to 30&deg;C (59&deg;F to 86&deg;F) in original foil pack</li>\n	<li>Please do not use if foil pack&nbsp;is broken</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>儲存於陰涼乾爽地方及原本鋁箔包裝內</li>\n	<li>如鋁箔包裝破損，請勿使用</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>储存于阴凉干爽地方及原本铝箔包装内</li>\n	<li>如铝箔包装破损，请勿使用</li>\n</ul>\n','For fast and effective relief of cold & flu symptoms:','有效迅速舒緩因普通感冒或流行性感冒症状：','有效迅速舒缓因普通感冒或流行性感冒症状：','','','','null','2015-05-04 04:33:41','2015-10-06 14:12:43','0000-00-00 00:00:00',1,'',0,'','','','','','',''),(32,'COLTALIN','幸福傷風素','幸福伤风素','Recovery forumla for colds, flu and allergy','收鼻水/抗過敏/傷風感冒配方','收鼻水/抗过敏/伤风感冒配方','<ul>\n	<li>Temporarily relief of cold &amp; flu or hay fever symptoms including minor aches and pains, sore throat, headache, runny nose, nasal congestion, fever, sneezing, itching eyes, nose or throat.</li>\n	<li>Aspirin free - less likely to cause gastric discomfort.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','<ul>\n	<li>舒緩因傷風感冒和花粉熱引起之症狀，包括輕微疼痛、喉嚨痛、頭痛、流鼻水、鼻塞、發燒、噴嚏、眼部、鼻腔或喉嚨痕癢等不適。</li>\n	<li>不含亞士匹靈，甚少引致腸胃不適。</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','<ul>\n	<li>舒缓因伤风感冒和花粉热引起之症状，包括轻微疼痛、喉咙痛、头痛、流鼻水、鼻塞、发烧、喷嚏、眼部、鼻腔或喉咙痕痒等不适。</li>\n	<li>不含阿司匹林，甚少引致肠胃不适。</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','IdLOWONDgoeryPr8C3o7QVhK1mSSGTy5.png','','',3,10,'NDC 51467-005-01',30,'<p>Available in packs of 24 tablets</p>\n','<ul>\n	<li>藥片</li>\n	<li>24片裝</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>药片</li>\n	<li>24片装</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>Age: </strong>Adults &amp; children 12 years and older &nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n<strong>Dosage and Administration:</strong>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Two tablets every 4 hours</li>\n	<li>While symptoms persist, not to exceed 6 doses (twelve tablets) in 24 hours</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>or</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>as directed by a doctor</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Age: </strong>Children 6 to under 12 years &nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n<strong>Dosage and Administration:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>One tablet every 4 hours</li>\n	<li>While symptoms persist, not to exceed 5 doses (five tablets) in 24 hours</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>or</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>as directed by a doctor</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Age:</strong> Children under 6 years &nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n<strong>Dosage and Administration: </strong>Consult a doctor</p>\n\n<p><strong>Remarks：Take each dose with plenty of water.</strong></p>\n','<p><strong>歲數：</strong>成人及12歲或以上兒童<br />\n<strong>劑量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每4小時服用兩片</li>\n	<li>如症狀持續，24小時內不可服用超過6劑(十二片)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>或</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>遵照醫生指示服食</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>歲數：</strong>6至12歲以下兒童<br />\n<strong>劑量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每4小時服用一片</li>\n	<li>如症狀持續，24小時內不可服用超過5劑(五片)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>或</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>遵照醫生指示服食</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>歲數：</strong>6歲以下兒童 &nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n<strong>劑量服法：</strong>遵照醫生指示服食</p>\n\n<p><strong>備註：服用時宜多飲開水。</strong></p>\n','<p><strong>岁数：</strong>成人及12岁或以上儿童<br />\n<strong>剂量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每4小时服用两片</li>\n	<li>如症状持续，24小时内不可服用超过6剂(十二片)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>或</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>遵照医生指示服食</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>岁数：</strong>6至12岁以下儿童<br />\n<strong>剂量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每4小时服用一片</li>\n	<li>如症状持续，24小时内不可服用超过5剂(五片)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>或</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>遵照医生指示服食</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>岁数：</strong>6岁以下儿童<br />\n<strong>剂量服法：</strong>遵照医生指示服食</p>\n\n<p><strong>备注：服用时宜多饮开水。</strong></p>\n','<p><strong>Each tablet contains:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Paracetamol (Acetaminophen) 325mg</strong><br />\nPurpose: Relieves pain &amp; fever</p>\n\n<p><strong>Chlorpheniramine Maleate 2mg</strong><br />\nPurpose:&nbsp;Relieves allergic symptoms such as runny nose, sneezing, watery eyes and itchy eyes</p>\n\n<p><strong>Phenylephrine Hydrochloride 5mg</strong><br />\nPurpose: Relieves nasal congestion and eases breathing</p>\n','<p><strong>每片含量：</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>撲熱息痛 (對乙酰氨基酚) 325毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 止痛退燒，減輕頭痛、肌肉酸痛及咽喉痛等症狀</p>\n\n<p><strong>馬來酸氯苯那敏 2毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒緩流鼻水、打噴嚏、淚眼及眼部痕癢等過敏症狀</p>\n\n<p><strong>鹽酸去氧腎上腺素 5毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒緩鼻塞，令呼吸更為暢順</p>\n','<p><strong>每片含量：</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>扑热息痛 (对乙酰氨基酚) 325毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 止痛退烧，减轻头痛、肌肉酸痛及咽喉痛等症状</p>\n\n<p><strong>马来酸氯苯那敏 2毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒缓流鼻水、打喷嚏、泪眼及眼部痕痒等过敏症状</p>\n\n<p><strong>盐酸去氧肾上腺素 5毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒缓鼻塞，令呼吸更为畅顺</p>\n','<ul>\n	<li>Liver warning: This product contains acetaminophen. Severe liver damage may occur if:\n	<ul>\n		<li>adult takes more than 12 tablets in 24 hours, which the maximum daily amount for this product</li>\n		<li>child takes more than 5 doses in 24 hours</li>\n		<li>taken with other drugs containing acetaminophen</li>\n		<li>adult has 3 or more alcoholic drinks everyday while using this product</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Do not use:\n	<ul>\n		<li>with any other drug containing acetaminophen (prescription or nonprescription). If you are not sure whether a drug contains acetaminophen, ask a doctor or pharmacist.</li>\n		<li>if you are now taking a prescription monoamine oxidase inhibitor (MAOI) (certain drugs for depression, psychiatric or emotional conditions, or Parkinson&rsquo;s disease). If you do not know whether a prescription drug contains an MAOI, ask a doctor or pharmacist.</li>\n		<li>for 2 weeks after stopping the MAOI drug</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Ask a doctor before use if the user has:\n	<ul>\n		<li>liver disease</li>\n		<li>heart disease</li>\n		<li>high blood pressure</li>\n		<li>thyroid disease</li>\n		<li>diabetes</li>\n		<li>glaucoma</li>\n		<li>difficulty in urination due to enlargement of the prostate gland</li>\n		<li>breathing problem such as emphysema or chronic bronchitis</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Ask a doctor or pharmacist before use if the user is:\n	<ul>\n		<li>taking the blood thinning drug warfarin</li>\n		<li>taking sedatives or tranquilizers</li>\n		<li>taking a prescription drug and you do not know if it contains an MAOI</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>When using this product:\n	<ul>\n		<li>do not exceed recommended dosage</li>\n		<li>may cause excitability especially in children</li>\n		<li>use caution when driving or operating machinery</li>\n		<li>avoid alcoholic beverages</li>\n		<li>may cause drowsiness;&nbsp;alcohol, sedatives, and tranquilizers may increase the drowsiness effect</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Stop use and ask a doctor if:\n	<ul>\n		<li>pain or nasal congestion gets worse or lasts more than 5 days (children) or 7 days (adults)</li>\n		<li>sore throat persists for more than 2 days</li>\n		<li>fever gets worse or lasts more than 3 days</li>\n		<li>nasal congestion is accompanied by fever</li>\n		<li>nervousness, dizziness, or sleeplessness occur</li>\n		<li>redness or swelling is present</li>\n		<li>new symptoms occur</li>\n		<li>any of the following occurs (these could be signs of a serious condition):&nbsp;severe sore throat;&nbsp;sore throat is accompanied or followed by fever, headache, rash, nausea or vomitting</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Do not give to children under 6 years of age unless directed by a doctor.</li>\n	<li>If pregnant or breast-feeding, ask a health professional before use.</li>\n	<li>Keep out of reach of children.</li>\n	<li>In case of overdose, get medical help or contact a Poison Control Center&nbsp;right away.&nbsp;Prompt medical attention is critical for adults as well as children even if you do not notice any signs or&nbsp;symptoms.</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>肝臟警告︰本產品含有對乙酰氨基酚。可導致肝臟嚴重損傷，如果︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>成人在24小時內服用超過十二片，這是本產品的最大日用量</li>\n		<li>兒童在24小時內服用超過5劑</li>\n		<li>與其他含有對乙酰氨基酚的藥物一起服用</li>\n		<li>成人在使用本產品時每日飲用3次以上的含酒精飲料</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>不能用於︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>與其他含有對乙酰氨基酚的藥物 (處方或非處方) 一起使用。如果您不確定某種藥物是否含有對乙酰氨基酚，請向醫生或藥劑師查詢。</li>\n		<li>如果您正在服用處方的單胺氧化酶抑制劑(MAOI) (用於治療抑鬱症、精神或情緒疾病或巴金森氏症的某些藥物)。如果您不確定某種處方藥物是否含有MAOI，請向醫生或藥劑師咨詢。</li>\n		<li>在停止MAOI藥物後達兩周</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>在使用前向醫生咨詢，如果使用者有︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>肝臟疾病</li>\n		<li>心臟病</li>\n		<li>高血壓</li>\n		<li>甲狀腺疾病</li>\n		<li>糖尿病</li>\n		<li>青光眼</li>\n		<li>因前列腺肥大引起的排尿困難</li>\n		<li>肺氣腫或慢性支氣管炎等呼吸疾病</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>在使用前向醫生或藥劑師咨詢，如果使用者正在︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>服用血液稀釋藥物殺鼠靈</li>\n		<li>服用安定或鎮靜藥物</li>\n		<li>服用處方藥物，而且不知道是否含有MAOI</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>在使用本產品時︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>切勿超過建議劑量</li>\n		<li>可能導致興奮性</li>\n		<li>特別是對於兒童而言</li>\n		<li>在開車或操作機器時要謹慎服用</li>\n		<li>避免含酒精飲料</li>\n		<li>可能導致嗜睡；酒精、安定藥物和鎮靜藥物可增加嗜睡作用</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>停止使用並向醫生咨詢，如果︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>疼痛或鼻塞變嚴重或持續超過5天(兒童)或7天(成人)</li>\n		<li>咽喉腫痛持續超過2天</li>\n		<li>發燒愈加嚴重或持續超過3天</li>\n		<li>鼻塞伴隨發燒</li>\n		<li>出現緊張不安、頭暈或失眠症狀</li>\n		<li>存在紅腫症狀</li>\n		<li>出現新症狀</li>\n		<li>出現任何以下症狀(這些可能是嚴重疾病的徵兆)︰嚴重喉嚨腫痛，咽喉腫痛伴隨發燒、頭痛、皮疹、噁心或嘔吐</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>除非醫生建議，切勿給6歲以下兒童服用。</li>\n	<li>如果懷孕或正在哺乳，請在使用前向醫療專業人員咨詢。</li>\n	<li>放置在兒童取不到的地方。</li>\n	<li>如果服用過量，請立即送醫或聯絡毒物控制中心。無論是對於成人或是對於兒童而言，迅速的醫療處理都是至關重要的，即使您沒有發現任何徵兆或症狀也是如此。</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>肝脏警告︰本产品含有对乙酰氨基酚。可导致肝脏严重损伤，如果︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>成人在24小时内服用超过十二片，这是本产品的最大日用量</li>\n		<li>儿童在24小时内服用超过5剂</li>\n		<li>与其他含有对乙酰氨基酚的药物一起服用</li>\n		<li>成人在使用本产品时每日饮用3次以上的含酒精饮料</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>不能用于︰\n	<ul>\n		<li>与其他含有对乙酰氨基酚的药物 (处方或非处方) 一起使用。如果您不确定某种药物是否含有对乙酰氨