到的地方。</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>Store below 25&deg;C in a dry place in the original foil pack</li>\n	<li>Do not use if the foil pack&nbsp;is broken</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>儲存於25&deg;C以下乾爽地方及原本鋁箔包裝內</li>\n	<li>如鋁箔包裝破損，請勿使用</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>储存于25&deg;C以下干爽地方及原本铝箔包装内</li>\n	<li>如铝箔包装破损，请勿使用</li>\n</ul>\n','For fast and effective relief of cold & flu symptoms:','有效迅速舒緩傷風感冒症狀：','有效迅速舒缓伤风感冒症状：','','','','critical','2015-06-30 10:09:35','2017-03-09 23:38:51','0000-00-00 00:00:00',1,'',0,'','','','','','',''),(31,'CHILDREN\'S COLTALIN','兒童幸福傷風素','儿童幸福伤风素','Cold & flu/Allergy formula','收鼻水/抗過敏/傷風感冒配方','收鼻水/抗过敏/伤风感冒配方','<ul>\n	<li>Fast and effective relief of symptoms of the common cold, fever, headache, mild to moderate aches and pains, sneezing, runny nose and nasal congestion.</li>\n	<li>Fruit flavor tablets, suitable for children 6 to under 12 years.</li>\n	<li>Aspirin free - less likely to cause gastric discomfort.</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>迅速舒緩感冒症狀、發燒、頭痛、輕微至中度疼痛、打噴嚏、流鼻水以及鼻塞。</li>\n	<li>菓子味藥片，專為6至12歲以下兒童而配製。</li>\n	<li>不含亞士匹靈，甚少引致腸胃不適。</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>迅速舒缓感冒症状、发烧、<span style=\"line-height:20.8px\">头痛、轻微至中度疼痛、</span><span style=\"line-height:20.8px\">打喷嚏、</span>流鼻水以及鼻塞。</li>\n	<li>菓子味药片，专为6至12岁以下儿童而配制。</li>\n	<li>不含阿司匹林，甚少引致肠胃不适。</li>\n</ul>\n','yRWM7na16bpfY4AJTZpwZiJVdb5s3GGJ.png','','',3,11,'2244264',0,'<p>Available in packs of 24 chewable tablets</p>\n','<ul>\n	<li>咀嚼片</li>\n	<li>24片裝</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>咀嚼<span style=\"line-height:1.6\">片</span></li>\n	<li>24片装</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>Age: </strong>Children 6 to under 12 years<br />\n<strong>Dosage and Administration:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Four tablets every 4 hours</li>\n	<li>Not to exceed sixteen tablets in 24 hours</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>歳數：</strong>6至12歲以下兒童<br />\n<strong>劑量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每4小時服用四片</li>\n	<li>24小時內不得服用超過十六片</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>歳数：</strong>6至12岁以下儿童<br />\n<strong>剂量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每4小时服用四片</li>\n	<li>24小时內不得服用超过十六片</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>Each tablet contains:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Paracetamol (Acetaminophen) 80mg</strong><br />\nPurpose: Relieves pain &amp; fever</p>\n\n<p><strong>Chlorpheniramine Maleate 0.5mg</strong><br />\nPurpose:&nbsp;Relieves allergic symptoms such as runny nose, sneezing, watery eyes and itchy eyes</p>\n\n<p><strong>Phenylephrine Hydrochloride 1.25mg</strong><br />\nPurpose: Relieves nasal congestion and eases breathing</p>\n','<p><strong>每片含量：</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>撲熱息痛 (對乙酰氨基酚) 80毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 止痛退燒，減輕頭痛、肌肉酸痛及咽喉痛等症狀</p>\n\n<p><strong>馬來酸氯苯那敏 0.5毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒緩流鼻水、打噴嚏、淚眼及眼部痕癢等過敏症狀</p>\n\n<p><strong>鹽酸去氧腎上腺素 1.25毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒緩鼻塞，令呼吸更為暢順</p>\n','<p><strong>每片含量：</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>扑热息痛 (对乙酰氨基酚) 80毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 止痛退烧，减轻头痛、肌肉酸痛及咽喉痛等症状</p>\n\n<p><strong>马来酸氯苯那敏 0.5毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒缓流鼻水、打喷嚏、泪眼及眼部痕痒等过敏症状</p>\n\n<p><strong>盐酸去氧肾上腺素 1.25毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒缓鼻塞，令呼吸更为畅顺</p>\n','<ul>\n	<li><strong>KEEP OUT OF THE REACH OF CHILDREN.</strong></li>\n	<li>Read the complete label prior to use and follow all label instructions.</li>\n	<li><strong>DO NOT USE</strong> this product in children under 6 years of age.</li>\n	<li><strong>DO NOT </strong>exceed the single and maximum daily dose. <strong>DO NOT USE</strong> for longer than 5 days. Taking more than the maximum daily dose may cause drowsiness, excitability and <strong>severe or possibly fatal liver damage</strong>.</li>\n	<li><strong>DO NOT USE</strong> with other drugs containing <strong>Acetaminophen</strong>, or any other cough and cold medications since harm may occur, unless recommended by a doctor.</li>\n	<li><strong>DO NOT USE</strong> if the child is allergic to any of the ingredients. Discontinue use if allergic reactions such as wheezing, rash or itching develop.</li>\n	<li>May cause drowsiness or excitability. <strong>DO NOT USE</strong> when child is engaged in activities requiring mental alertness.</li>\n	<li>Consult a doctor if symptoms worsen, last for more than 5 days, or fever lasts more than 3 days, or are accompanied by a high fever (&gt;38&deg;C) or the production of thick yellow/green phlegm.</li>\n	<li>Ask a doctor or a pharmacist before use if the child:\n	<ul>\n		<li>has a serious liver or kidney disease, chronic lung disease, heart or thyroid disease, high blood pressure, diabetes, difficulty in urination or glaucoma;</li>\n		<li>uses any other medications including natural health products, prescription drugs, nonprescription drugs, salicylates or other pain and fever relief medications (nonsteroidal anti-inflammatory drugs (NSAIDS)).</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Side effects may include: allergic reaction, breathing difficulties, convulsions, drowsiness, hallucinations, and rapid heart rate.</li>\n	<li><strong>In case of overdose:</strong> Call a Poison Control Centre or doctor immediately, even if you do not notice any signs or symptoms. Within the first 24 hours you may experience increased sweating, nausea, vomiting, stomach pain, and loss of appetite.</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li><strong>請將此藥物放在兒童不能接觸到的地方。</strong></li>\n	<li>服用本藥前請先閱讀本標簽，並跟從指示服用本藥。</li>\n	<li>6歲以下兒童切勿服用本藥。</li>\n	<li><strong>切勿</strong>服食超過建議個別劑量及每日最高劑量。切勿服食超過5天。服用超過每日最高劑量可能引致嗜睡、興奮性、<strong>嚴重甚至可能致命的肝臟損傷</strong>。</li>\n	<li>除非醫生建議，<strong>不可</strong>同時服用其他含有<strong>撲熱息痛</strong>的藥物，或其他傷風感冒和咳嗽藥物。</li>\n	<li>對本藥任何成分過敏者<strong>不可服用</strong>。如服後出現喘氣、紅腫或痕癢，必須停止服用本藥。</li>\n	<li>此藥可使人昏昏欲睡或興奮。如需要進行任何保持警覺的活動，<strong>不可服用</strong>本藥。</li>\n	<li>服用後若症狀轉差、持續超過5天、發燒持續超過3天、伴隨高燒 (&gt;38&deg;C)或出現呈黃/綠色的濃痰，請立即尋求醫生意見。</li>\n	<li>如屬以下情況，服用前應請示醫生或藥劑師：\n	<ul>\n		<li>患有嚴重肝病或腎病、長期肝病、心臟或甲狀腺疾病、高血壓、糖尿病、排尿困難或青光眼</li>\n		<li>正在服食其他藥物包括天然保健產品、處方藥物、非處方藥物、水楊酸或其他止痛退熱藥物(非類固醇消炎止痛藥, NSAIDS)。</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>本藥可能引致以下不良反應︰過敏反應、呼吸困難、抽搐、昏昏欲睡、幻覺和心率加快。</li>\n	<li><strong>如果服用過量</strong>，即使沒有出現任何迹像或症狀，亦必須立即聯絡毒物管制中心 (Poison Control Centre) 或醫生。服用過量後首24小時可能會增加流汗、噁心、嘔吐、胃痛和食慾不振。</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','<ul>\n	<li><strong>请将此药物放在儿童不能接触到的地方。</strong></li>\n	<li>服用本药前请先阅读本标签，并跟从指示服用本药。</li>\n	<li>6岁以下儿童切勿服用本药。</li>\n	<li><strong>切勿</strong>服食超过建议个别剂量及每日最高剂量。切勿服食超过5天。服用超过每日最高剂量可能引致嗜睡、兴奋性、<strong>严重甚至可能致命的肝脏损伤</strong>。</li>\n	<li>除非医生建议，<strong>不可</strong>同时服用其他含有<strong>扑热息痛</strong>的药物，或其他伤风感冒和咳嗽药物。</li>\n	<li>对本药任何成分过敏者<strong>不可服用</strong>。如服后出现喘气、红肿或痕痒，必须停止服用本药。</li>\n	<li>此药可使人昏昏欲睡或兴奋。如需要进行任何保持警觉的活动，<strong>不可服用</strong>本药。</li>\n	<li>服用后若症状转差、持续超过5天、发烧持续超过3天、伴随高烧(&gt;38&deg;C)或出现呈黄/绿色的浓痰，请立即寻求医生意见。</li>\n	<li>如属以下情况，服用前应请示医生或药剂师：\n	<ul>\n		<li>患有严重肝病或肾病、长期肝病、心脏或甲状腺疾病、高血压、糖尿病、排尿困难或青光眼</li>\n		<li>正在服食其他药物包括天然保健产品、处方药物、非处方药物、水杨酸或其他止痛退热药物(非类固醇消炎止痛药, NSAIDS)。</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>本药可能引致以下不良反应︰过敏反应、呼吸困难、抽搐、昏昏欲睡、幻觉和心率加快。</li>\n	<li><strong>如果服用过量</strong>，即使没有出现任何迹像或症状，亦必须立即联络毒物管制中心(Poison Control Centre) 或医生。服用过量后首24小时可能会增加流汗、恶心、呕吐、胃痛和食欲不振。</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','<p>Store between 15&deg;C to 30&deg;C (59&deg;F to 86&deg;F) in original foil pack<br />\nPlease do not use if&nbsp;foil pack&nbsp;is broken</p>\n','<p>儲存於陰涼乾爽地方及原本鋁箔包裝內<br />\n如鋁箔包裝破損，請勿使用</p>\n','<p>储存于阴凉干爽地方及原本铝箔包装内<br />\n如铝箔包装破损，请勿使用</p>\n','Temporarily relief of common cold symptoms:','舒緩感冒症狀：','舒缓感冒症状：','','','','','2015-09-14 12:20:30','2017-01-26 22:54:40','0000-00-00 00:00:00',1,'Children Series',0,'','','','','','',''),(27,'MAGSIL LEMON MINT','胃的素 檸檬薄荷','胃的素 柠檬薄荷','Antacid/Anti-flatulent','解胃酸/化胃氣','解胃酸/化胃氣','<ul>\n	<li>Effective relief of heartburn, dyspepsia, hyperacidity, flatulence and stomach pain associated with these conditions.</li>\n	<li>Non-constipating.</li>\n	<li>Sugar free.</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>舒緩胃灼熱、消化不良、胃酸過多、胃氣脹及因上述情況引起的胃痛。</li>\n	<li>不會引致便秘。</li>\n	<li>不含糖份，適合戒糖人士服用。</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>舒缓胃灼热、消化不良、胃酸过多、胃气胀及因上述情况引起的胃痛。</li>\n	<li>不会引致便秘。</li>\n	<li>不含糖份，适合戒糖人士服用。</li>\n</ul>\n','DjooMpIj8yT6k1tGA28tWKXbxR65ZE6V.png','','',1,3,' HK-53146',20,'<ul>\n	<li>Available in pack of 24 chewable tablets</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>咀嚼片</li>\n	<li>24片裝</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>咀嚼片</li>\n	<li>24片裝</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>Age:&nbsp;</strong>Adults and children 12 years and older<br />\n<strong>Dosage and Administration:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Two tablets to be well chewed 30 minutes after meals, at bedtime or when symptoms occur&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Not to exceed twenty four tablets in 24 hours</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>OR</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>As directed by physician</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Age:&nbsp;</strong>Children under 12 years<br />\n<strong>Dosage and Administration:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Consult your doctor before use</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>歳數：</strong>成人及12歲或以上兒童<br />\n<strong>劑量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:none\">\n	<li>餐後30分鐘、睡前或胃部不適時，完全嚼碎兩片</li>\n	<li>24小時內不可服用超過二十四片</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>或</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>按醫生指示服用</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>歳數：</strong>12歲以下兒童<br />\n<strong>劑量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>服用前應先諮詢醫生意見</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>岁数：</strong>成人及12岁或以上儿童<br />\n<strong>剂量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>餐後30分钟、睡前或胃部不适时，完全嚼碎两片</li>\n	<li>24小时内不可服用超过二十四片</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>或</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>按医生指示服用</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>岁数：</strong>12岁以下儿童<br />\n<strong>剂量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>服用前应先咨询医生意见</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>Each tablet contains:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Aluminium Hydroxide Dried Gel 200mg<br />\nMagnesium Hydroxide 200mg</strong><br />\nPurpose: Neutralize the gastric acid and relieve gastric discomfort caused by stomach acid.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Dimethylpolysiloxane 20mg</strong><br />\nPurpose:&nbsp;Disperses the accumulated gas that often causes indigestion and stomach pain.</p>\n','<p><strong>每片含量：</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>氫氧化鋁乾凝膠200毫克<br />\n氧化鎂200毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 中和胃酸和舒緩胃酸引致的胃部不適</p>\n\n<p><strong>二甲基聚硅氧烷 20毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 化解經常引起消化不良和胃痛的胃氣</p>\n','<p><strong>每片含量：</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>氢氧化铝乾凝胶 200毫克<br />\n氢氧化镁 200毫克</strong><br />\n用途:&nbsp;中和胃酸和舒缓胃酸引致的胃部不适</p>\n\n<p><strong>二甲基聚硅氧烷 20毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 化解经常引起消化不良和胃疼的胃气</p>\n','<ul>\n	<li>Consult your doctor before use if&nbsp;you are receiving prescribed medications.</li>\n	<li>Do not take this product if you are:\n	<ul>\n		<li>hypersensitive to any ingredient or this product</li>\n		<li>severely debilitated</li>\n		<li>suffering from kidney failure or hypophosphatemia</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>This product may cause gastrointestinal disturbance but uncommon.</li>\n	<li>Do not exceed the stated dose.</li>\n	<li>Keep this drug out of reach of children.</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>如正在服用醫生處方藥物，服用本藥前應先諮詢醫生意見。</li>\n	<li>屬以下情況者不可服用：\n	<ul>\n		<li>對本藥任何成分會產生過敏反應</li>\n		<li>嚴重衰弱</li>\n		<li>腎病或低磷血症患者</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>本藥可能會引致腸胃失調，但不常見。</li>\n	<li>切勿服食超過指定劑量。</li>\n	<li>請將此藥放在兒童不能接觸到的地方 。</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>如正在服用医生处方药物，服用本药前应先咨询医生意见。</li>\n	<li>属以下情况者不可服用：\n	<ul>\n		<li>对本药任何成分会产生过敏反应</li>\n		<li>严重衰弱</li>\n		<li>肾病或低磷血症患者</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>本药可能会引致肠胃失调，但不常见。</li>\n	<li>切勿服食超过指定剂量。</li>\n	<li>请将此药放在儿童不能接触到的地方 。</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>Store below 25&deg;C in a dry place in the original foil pack</li>\n	<li>Do not use if the foil pack&nbsp;is broken</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>儲存於25&deg;C以下乾爽地方及原本鋁箔包裝內</li>\n	<li>如鋁箔包裝破損，請勿使用</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>储存于25&deg;C以下干爽地方及原本铝箔包装内</li>\n	<li>如鋁箔包装破损，请勿使用</li>\n</ul>\n','For fast and effective relief of:','有效迅速舒緩：','有效迅速舒缓：','','','','null','2015-07-02 02:48:11','2015-10-01 13:45:54','0000-00-00 00:00:00',1,'',0,'','','','','','',''),(29,'AULZADIN','幸福衛適定','幸福卫适定','Gastric acid suppressant','抑制胃酸分泌','抑制胃酸分泌','<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"line-height:18.9091px\">Act through inhibition of gastric acid secretion; a multi-purpose medicine for stomach disorders.&nbsp;</span></li>\n	<li>Fast symptomatic relief of stomach pain, hyperacidity, dyspepsia, heartburn and gastro-oesophageal reflux disease, and prevention of these symptoms&nbsp;associated with food and beverage.</li>\n	<li>&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>It contains Famotidine, a highly effective and long-acting histamine H2-receptor antagonist which effectively reduces gastric secretion. Aulzadin acts as an antiulcerant by reducing the acid and pepsin secretion.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"line-height:18.9091px\">通過抑制胃酸分泌發揮效用，是多功能胃藥</span>。</li>\n	<li>快速舒緩胃痛、胃酸過多、消化不良、胃灼熱、胃酸倒流<span style=\"line-height:18.9091px\">症狀，以及預防飲食引起上述症狀。</span></li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>通过抑制胃酸分泌发挥效用，是多功能胃药。</li>\n	<li>快速舒缓胃痛、胃酸过多、消化不良、胃灼热、胃酸倒流症状，以及预防饮食引起上述症状。</li>\n</ul>\n','I7i81dq3raGgDJkxMOvg7hhAcRA1FY3Z.png','','',1,3,'HK-47573',20,'<ul>\n	<li>Available in pack of 8 tablets</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>藥片</li>\n	<li>8片裝</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>药片</li>\n	<li>8片装</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>For</strong><strong> gastro-esophageal reflux disease</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>One tablet to be taken twice daily</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>For stomach pain, hyperacidity, dyspepsia, heartburn and prevention of symptoms associated with food and beverages</strong><br />\nAdults and children over 12 years</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>For relief: One half to one tablet to be taken as needed</li>\n	<li>For prevention: One half to one tablet to be taken 30 minutes before eating, or 1 hour before evening meal (if expect to interfere with sleep)</li>\n	<li>Not to exceed one tablet in 24 hours</li>\n	<li>Or as directed by physician</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Benign Gastric Ulcer&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Two tablets to be taken daily at night</li>\n	<li>Treatment should be given for 4-8 weeks</li>\n	<li>Duration of treatment may be shortened if endoscopy reveals that the ulcer has healed</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>For duodenal </strong><strong>u</strong><strong>lcer&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Initial therapy</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Two tablets to be taken daily at night</li>\n	<li>Treatment should be given for 4-8 weeks</li>\n	<li>Duration of treatment may be shortened if endoscopy reveals that the ulcer has healed</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Maintenance therapy</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>One tablets to be taken daily at night</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>For Zollinger-Ellison Syndrome</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>One tablet to be taken every 6 hours</li>\n	<li>Adjust dose to as directed by physician</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>舒緩胃酸倒流症狀</strong><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每天服2次，每次一片</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>舒緩</strong><strong>胃痛、胃酸過多、消化不良、胃灼熱，以及預防飲食引起上述症狀</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>成人及</strong><strong>12</strong><strong>歲以上兒童</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>為舒緩症狀︰有需要時服半片至一片</li>\n	<li>為預防症狀︰進食前30分鐘，或進食晚餐前1小時服用 (如認為症狀會妨礙睡眠)</li>\n	<li>24小時內不可服用超過一片</li>\n	<li>或依照醫生指示服食</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>良性胃潰瘍</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每晚服兩片</li>\n	<li>治療4至8星期</li>\n	<li>如內視鏡檢顯示潰瘍已經痊癒，則療程可以縮短</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>十二指腸潰瘍</strong><br />\n<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;起始治療</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每晚服兩片</li>\n	<li>治療4至8星期</li>\n	<li>如內視鏡檢顯示潰瘍已經痊癒，則療程可以縮短。大部份的病例中十二指腸潰瘍可於4星期內治療</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 維持治療</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每晚服一片</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>卓</strong><strong>-</strong><strong>艾二氏綜合症</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每6小時服一片</li>\n	<li>依照醫生指示調整劑量</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>舒缓胃酸倒流症状</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每天服2次，每次一片</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>舒缓胃痛、胃酸过多、消化不良、胃灼热，以及预防饮食引起上述症状</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>成人及</strong><strong>12</strong><strong>岁以上儿童</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>为舒缓症状︰有需要时服半片至一片</li>\n	<li>为预防症状︰进食前30分钟，或进食晚餐前1小时服用 (如认为症状会妨碍睡眠)</li>\n	<li>24小时内不可服用超过一片</li>\n	<li>或依照医生指示服食</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>良性胃溃疡</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每晚服两片</li>\n	<li>治疗4至8星期</li>\n	<li>如内视镜检显示溃疡已经痊愈，则疗程可以缩短</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>十二指肠溃疡</strong><br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>起始治疗</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每晚服两片</li>\n	<li>治疗4至8星期</li>\n	<li>如内视镜检显示溃疡已经痊愈，则疗程可以缩短。大部份的病例中十二指肠溃疡可于4星期内治疗</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>维持治疗</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每晚服一片</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>卓</strong><strong>-</strong><strong>艾二氏综合症</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每6小时服一片</li>\n	<li>依照医生指示调整剂量</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','<p><strong>Each tablet contains: </strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Famotidine 20mg&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong>&nbsp;<br />\nPurposes: Inhibits secretion of gastric acid and pepsin</p>\n','<p><strong>每片含量：</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>法莫替丁 20毫克&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><br />\n用途：抑制胃酸和胃蛋白分泌</p>\n','<p><strong>每片含量：</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>法莫替丁 20毫克</strong><br />\n用途：抑制胃酸和胃蛋白分泌</p>\n','<ul>\n	<li>Do not exceed the stated dose.</li>\n	<li>Gastric Neoplasm:\n	<ul>\n		<li>Gastric malignancy should be excluded prior to initiation of therapy of peptic ulcer with Aulzadin.</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Renal Dysfunction:\n	<ul>\n		<li>A reduction in daily dosage should be considered if creatinine clearance falls below 10ml/min.</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Use in pregnancy:\n	<ul>\n		<li>Not recommended for use in pregnancy.</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Nursing Mothers:\n	<ul>\n		<li>Famotidine is detectable in human milk. Nursing mothers should either stop using this drug or stop nursing.</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Use in children:\n	<ul>\n		<li>Safety and effectiveness of use in children has not been established.</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Use in the elderly:\n	<ul>\n		<li>No dosage adjustment is required based on age alone.</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Do not take this product if you are hypersensitive to any ingredient of this product.</li>\n	<li>Keep this drug out of the reach of children.</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>切勿服用超過指定劑量。</li>\n	<li>胃腫瘤患：\n	<ul>\n		<li>使用本藥品治療胃潰瘍前，必須先排除患有惡性胃癌之可能性。</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>&nbsp;腎功能不良患者：\n	<ul>\n		<li>如果肌酐清除率(Creatinine Clearance)降低至10ml/min，則必須考慮降低每天之劑量。</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>孕婦：\n	<ul>\n		<li>不建議孕婦使用本藥。</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>授乳婦女：\n	<ul>\n		<li>法莫替丁可由人類乳汁檢出，授乳婦女宜先停用本藥才繼續授乳，或停止授乳。</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>兒童：\n	<ul>\n		<li>用於孩童之效率及安全性尚未建立。</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>老人：\n	<ul>\n		<li>不需随著年齡之不同而調整劑量。</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>對本藥任何成分過敏者不可服用。</li>\n	<li>請將此藥物放在兒童不能接觸到的地方。</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>切勿服用超过指定剂量。</li>\n	<li>胃肿瘤患：\n	<ul>\n		<li>使用本药品治疗胃溃疡前，必须先排除患有恶性胃癌之可能性。</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>肾功能不良患者：\n	<ul>\n		<li>如果肌酐清除率(Creatinine Clearance)降低至10ml/min，则必须考虑降低每天之剂量。</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>孕妇：\n	<ul>\n		<li>不建议孕妇使用本药。</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>授乳妇女：\n	<ul>\n		<li>法莫替丁可由人类乳汁检出，授乳妇女宜先停用本药才继续授乳，或停止授乳。</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>儿童：\n	<ul>\n		<li>用于孩童之效率及安全性尚未建立。</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>老人：\n	<ul>\n		<li>不需随着年龄之不同而调整剂量。</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>对本药任何成分过敏者不可服用。</li>\n	<li>请将此药物放在儿童不能接触到的地方。</li>\n</ul>\n','<p>Store below 25&deg;C in a dry place in the original foil pack<br />\nDo not use if the foil pack&nbsp;is broken</p>\n','<p>儲存於25&deg;C以下乾爽地方及原本鋁箔包裝內<br />\n如鋁箔包裝破損，請勿使用</p>\n','<p>储存于25&deg;C以下干爽地方及原本铝箔包装内<br />\n如铝箔包装破损，请勿使用</p>\n','For symptomatic relief and prevention of:','舒緩及預防︰','舒缓及预防：','','','','critical','2015-08-07 09:00:27','2015-10-02 04:03:58','0000-00-00 00:00:00',1,'',0,'','','','','','',''),(30,'NT-DIOREA','幸福瀉利治','幸福泻利治','A must-have for travelers','旅行必備良藥','旅行必备良药','<p>Fast relief of sudden or occasional diarrhea, including traveler&#39;s diarrhea.</p>\n','<p>適用於因水土不服引起之肚瀉及偶發性之腹瀉。</p>\n','<p>适用于因水土不服引起之肚泻及偶发性之腹泻。</p>\n','1FyB0CfG9VK3aIrz300ky1SpzSnBpo8k.png','','',1,3,'HK-47609',10,'<ul>\n	<li>Available in pack of 12 tablets</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>藥片</li>\n	<li>12片裝</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>药片</li>\n	<li>12片装</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>Age: </strong>Adults and children over 12 years&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n<strong>Dosage and Administration:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Initially two tablets followed by one tablet after each unformed stool</li>\n	<li>Not to exceed eight tablets in 24 hours</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Age:</strong> Children 9-12 years&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n<strong>Dosage and Administration:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Initially one tablet followed by 1one tablet after each unformed stool</li>\n	<li>Not to exceed four tablets in 24 hours</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Age:</strong> Children 5-8 years&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n<strong>Dosage and Administration:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Initially one half tablet followed by one half tablet after each unformed stool</li>\n	<li>Not to exceed two tablets in 24 hours</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>歲數：</strong>成人及12歲以上兒童&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n<strong>劑量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>首次服兩片，如肚瀉持續時，每次瀉後再服一片</li>\n	<li>24小時內不可服用超過八片</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>歲數：</strong>9至12歲兒童<br />\n<strong>劑量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>首次服一片，如肚瀉持續時，每次瀉後再服一片</li>\n	<li>24小時內不可服用超過四片</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>歲數：</strong>5至8歲兒童<br />\n<strong>劑量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>首次服半片，如肚瀉持續時，每次瀉後再服半片</li>\n	<li>24小時內不可服用超過兩片</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>岁数：</strong>成人及12岁以上儿童<br />\n<strong>剂量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>首次服两片，如肚泻持续时，每次泻后再服一片</li>\n	<li>24小时内不可服用超过8片</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>岁数：</strong>9至12岁儿童<br />\n<strong>剂量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>首次服一片，如肚泻持续时，每次泻后再服一片</li>\n	<li>24小时内不可服用超过四片</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>岁数：</strong>5至8岁儿童<br />\n<strong>剂量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>首次服半片，如肚泻持续时，每次泻后再服半片</li>\n	<li>24小时内不可服用超过两片</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>Each tablet contains: </strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Loperamide Hydrochloride 2mg&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><br />\nPurposes: Anti diarrhea</p>\n','<p><strong>每片含量：</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>鹽酸洛哌丁胺2毫克&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n用途：止腹瀉</p>\n','<p><strong>每片含量：</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>盐酸洛哌丁胺2毫克</strong><br />\n用途：止腹泻</p>\n','<ul>\n	<li><strong>NT-Diorea</strong> is safe and reliable if &lsquo;<strong>Dosage and Administration</strong>&rsquo; is observed. Do not exceed the stated dose.</li>\n	<li>Consult your doctor before use if:\n	<ul>\n		<li>you have high fever, or if blood is present in the stool.</li>\n		<li>your are hypersensitive to Loperamide</li>\n		<li>you are pregnant or are nursing baby</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Keep this drug out of the reach of children.</li>\n	<li>NT-Diorea is contraindicated in patients who are hypersensitive to any ingredients of this product.</li>\n	<li>Not recommended for diarrhea caused by infection because it may delay the expulsion of harmful substance from the bowel.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','<ul>\n	<li>依照劑量服法指示服用幸福瀉利治是非常安全可靠的</li>\n	<li>切勿服用超過指定劑量</li>\n	<li>如屬以下情況，服用前應請示醫生：\n	<ul>\n		<li>如肚瀉同時發高燒或大便有血</li>\n		<li>對洛丁胺有過敏反應</li>\n		<li>懷孕或哺乳期間</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>請將此藥物放置在兒童不能拿取的地方</li>\n	<li>對本藥任何成份會產生過敏反應者忌服</li>\n	<li>不建議使用於感染產生的腹瀉，以免延遲需由腸排出有害的物質</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>依照剂量服法指示服用幸福泻利治是非常安全可靠的</li>\n	<li>切勿服用超过指定剂量</li>\n	<li>如属以下情况，服用前应请示医生：\n	<ul>\n		<li>如肚泻同时发高烧或大便有血</li>\n		<li>对洛丁胺有过敏反应</li>\n		<li>怀孕或哺乳期间</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>请将此药物放置在儿童不能拿取的地方</li>\n	<li>对本药任何成份会产生过敏反应者忌服</li>\n	<li>不建议使用于感染产生的腹泻，以免延迟需由肠排出有害的物质</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','<ul>\n	<li>Store below 25&deg;C in a dry place in the original foil pack</li>\n	<li>Do not use if the foil pack&nbsp;is broken</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>儲存於25&deg;C以下乾爽地方及原本鋁箔包裝內</li>\n	<li>如鋁箔包裝破損，請勿使用</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>储存于25℃以下干爽地方及原本铝箔包装内</li>\n	<li>如铝箔包装破损，请勿使用</li>\n</ul>\n','','','','','','','onset','2015-08-07 09:47:48','2015-10-01 14:01:22','0000-00-00 00:00:00',1,'',0,'','','','','','',''),(33,'COLTALIN-ND','無睡意幸福傷風素','无睡意幸福伤风素','Extra strength cold & sinus formula','特強退熱鎮痛/通鼻塞/感冒配方','特强退热镇痛/通鼻塞/感冒配方','<ul>\n	<li>Non-drowsy formula. Suitable for people who need to work and stay alert whist taking the medication.</li>\n	<li>Temporarily relief of cold &amp; flu or hay fever symptoms including minor aches and pains, sore throat, sinus congestion, headache, nasal congestion and fever.</li>\n	<li>Aspirin free - less likely to cause gastric discomfort.</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	