rong>岁数：</strong>​6至12岁以下儿童<br />\n​<strong>剂量服法：</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>每4小时服用一片</li>\n	<li>如症状持续，24小时内不可服用超过5剂(五片)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>或</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>遵照医生指示服食</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>岁数：</strong>6岁以下儿童<br />\n<strong>剂量服法：</strong>遵照医生指示服食</p>\n','<p><strong>Each tablet contains:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Paracetamol (Acetaminophen) 325mg</strong><br />\nPurpose: Relieves pain &amp; fever</p>\n\n<p><strong>Phenylephrine Hydrochloride 5mg</strong><br />\nPurpose: Relieves nasal congestion and eases breathing</p>\n','<p><strong>每片含量：</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>撲熱息痛 (對乙酰氨基酚) 325毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 止痛退燒，減輕頭痛、肌肉酸痛及咽喉痛等症狀</p>\n\n<p><strong>鹽酸去氧腎上腺素 5毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒緩鼻塞，令呼吸更為暢順</p>\n','<p><strong>每片含量：</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>扑热息痛 (对乙酰氨基酚) 325毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 止痛退烧，减轻头痛、肌肉酸痛及咽喉痛等症状</p>\n\n<p><strong>盐酸去氧肾上腺素 5毫克</strong><br />\n用途: 舒缓鼻塞，令呼吸更为畅顺</p>\n','<ul>\n	<li>Liver warning: This product contains acetaminophen. Severe liver damage may occur if:\n	<ul>\n		<li>adult takes more than 12 tablets in 24 hours, which the maximum daily amount for this product</li>\n		<li>child takes more than 5 doses in 24 hours</li>\n		<li>taken with other drugs containing acetaminophen</li>\n		<li>adult has 3 or more alcoholic drinks everyday while using this product</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Do not use:\n	<ul>\n		<li>with any other drug containing acetaminophen (prescription or nonprescription). If you are not sure whether a drug contains acetaminophen, ask a doctor or pharmacist.</li>\n		<li>For fever for more than 3 days, unless directed by a physician.</li>\n		<li>if you are now taking a prescription monoamine oxidase inhibitor (MAOI) (certain drugs for depression, psychiatric or emotional conditions, or Parkinson&rsquo;s disease). If you do not know whether a prescription drug contains an MAOI, ask a doctor or pharmacist.</li>\n		<li>for 2 weeks after stopping the MAOI drug</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Ask a doctor before use if the user has:\n	<ul>\n		