状也是如此。</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>Store below 25&deg;C&nbsp;in a dry place in the original foil pack</li>\n	<li>Do not use if the foil pack&nbsp;is broken</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>儲存於25&deg;C以下乾爽地方及原本鋁箔包裝內</li>\n	<li>如鋁箔包裝破損，請勿使用</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','<ul>\n	<li>储存于25&deg;C阴凉干爽地方及原本铝箔包装内</li>\n	<li>如铝箔包装破损，请勿使用</li>\n</ul>\n','Temporarily relief of cold & flu or hay fever symptoms:','舒緩傷風感冒和花粉熱症狀：','舒缓伤风感冒和花粉热症状：','','','','onset','2015-09-14 13:03:08','2017-02-09 22:53:56','0000-00-00 00:00:00',1,'',0,'','','','','','',''),(34,'FORTOLIN','幸福止痛素','幸福止痛素','Safe and effective analgesic & antipyretic','安全有效止痛退熱配方','安全有效止痛退热配方','<ul>\n	<li>Safe and fast acting analgesic &amp; antipyretic.</li>\n	<li>Effective relief of minor aches and pains associated with the common code, including headache, toothache, muscular aches and fever.</li>\n	<li>Ingredient widely used by medical professionals.</li>\n	<li>Aspirin free - less likely to cause gastric discomfort</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>止痛退熱，安全快捷。</li>\n	<li>有效舒緩輕微痛症與感冒引起的疼痛，包括頭痛、牙痛、肌肉酸痛和發燒。</li>\n	<li>所含成份最為醫學界選用。</li>\n	<li>不含亞士匹靈，甚少引致腸胃不適。</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>止痛退热，安全快捷。</li>\n	<li>有效舒缓轻微痛症与感冒引起的疼痛，包括头痛、牙痛、肌肉酸痛和发烧。</li>\n	<li>所含成份最为医学界选用。</li>\n	<li>不含阿司匹林，甚少引致肠胃不适。</li>\n</ul>\n','OzAykjD6JDdDyU407oCJn1EyS1RGDbYS.png','','',3,10,'NDC 51467-127-24',10,'<p>Available in packs of 24 tablets</p>\n','<ul>\n	<li>藥片</li>\n	<li>24片裝</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li>药片</li>\n	<li>24片装</li>\n</ul>\n','<p><strong>Age:</strong> Adults &amp; children 12 years and older<br />\n<strong>Dosage and Administration:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>One tablet every 3 to 4 hours</li>\n	<li>While symptoms persist, two tablets every 6 hours</li>\n	<li>Not to exceed eight tablets in 24 hours</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>OR</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>As directed by a doctor</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Age: </strong>Children under 12 years &nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n<strong>Dosage and Administration: </strong>Consult a doctor</p>\n','<p><strong>歲數：</strong>成人及12歲或以上兒童 &