c to Acetaminophen.</li>\n	<li><strong>Consult a doctor if:</strong>\n	<ul>\n		<li>you develop allergic reactions such as wheezing, rash or itching;</li>\n		<li>your symptoms last for more than 5 days, or fever lasts more than 3 days.</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Ask a doctor or a pharmacist before use if you:\n	<ul>\n		<li>are pregnant or breastfeeding;</li>\n		<li>have chronic alcoholism;</li>\n		<li>have a serious liver or kidney disease;</li>\n		<li>use any other medications including natural health products, prescription drugs, salicylates or other pain and fever relief medications (nonsteroidal anti-inflammatory drugs (NSAIDS)).</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><strong>In case of overdose:</strong> Call a Poison Control Centre or doctor immediately, even if you do not notice any signs or symptoms. Within the first 24 hours you may experience increased sweating, nausea, vomiting, stomach pain, and loss of appetite.</li>\n</ul>\n','<ul>\n	<li><strong>請將此藥物放在兒童不能接觸到的地方。</strong></li>\n	<li><strong>不可</strong>同時服用其他含有<strong>撲熱息痛</strong>的藥物。</li>\n	<li><strong>只供成人及</strong><strong>12歲或以上兒童服用。</strong>除非醫生建議，<strong>切勿</strong>服食超過建議劑量。服用最少有效劑量。服用超過每日最高劑量可能引致嗜睡、興奮性、<strong>嚴重甚至可能致命的肝臟損傷</strong>。</li>\n	<li>對撲熱息痛過敏者<strong>不可服用</strong>。</li>\n	<li>服藥後如出現以下情況，請尋求醫生意見：\n	<ul>\n		<li>過敏反應如喘氣、紅腫或痕癢</li>\n		<li>症狀持續超過5天，或發燒超過3天</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>如屬以下情況，服用前應請示醫生或藥劑師：\n	<ul>\n		<li>懷孕或哺乳期間</li>\n		<li>長期飲酒</li>\n		<li>患有嚴重肝病或腎病</li>\n		<li>正在服食其他藥物包括天然保健產品、處方藥物、非處方藥物、水楊酸或其他止痛退熱藥物(非類固醇消炎止痛藥, NSAIDS)</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><strong>如果服用過量</strong>，即使沒有出現任何迹像或症狀，亦必須立即聯絡毒物管制中心 (Poison Control Centre) 或醫生。服用過量後首24小時可能會增加流汗、噁心、嘔吐、胃痛和食慾不振。</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','<ul>\n	<li>​<strong>请将此药物放在儿童不能接触到的地方。</strong></li>\n	<li><strong>不可</strong>同时服用其他含有<strong>扑热息痛</strong>的药物。</li>\n	<li><strong>只供成人及</strong><strong>12岁或以上儿童服用。</strong>除非医生建议，<strong>切勿</strong>服食超过建议剂量。服用最少有效剂量。服用超过每日最高剂量可能引致嗜睡、兴奋性、<strong>严重甚至可能致命的肝脏损伤</strong>。</li>\n	<li>对扑热息痛过敏者<strong>不可服用</st